(93, 'S ra i ca on thanh nin Cng sn H Ch Minh', 's-ra-i-ca-oan-thanh-nien-cng-sn-h-chi-minh', '', '<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<span class="submitted"> <span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Arial;"><img alt="" src="http://ulis.vnu.edu.vn/sites/default/files/huyieuDoan_N%281%29.gif" height="112" hspace="10" vspace="10" width="100" align="left" />\r\n<div style="margin: 6pt 0cm 0pt; line-height: 150%; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Arial;">Ma xun nm 1931, t ngy 20 n ngy 26/3, ti Hi ngh Ban chp hnh Trung ng ng ln th 2, Trung ng ng  ginh mt phn quan trng trong chng trnh lm vic  bn v cng tc thanh nin v i n nhng quyt nh c  ngha c bit, nh cc cp y ng t Trung ng n a phng phi c ngay cc y vin ca ng ph trch cng tc on.</span></div>\r\n<div style="margin: 6pt 0cm 0pt; line-height: 150%; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Arial;">Trc s pht trin ln mnh ca on trn c 3 min Bc, Trung, Nam,  nc ta xut hin nhiu t chc on c s vi khong 1.500 on vin v mt s a phng  hnh thnh t chc on t x, huyn n c s. S pht trin ln mnh ca on  p ng kp thi nhng i hi cp bch ca phong tro thanh nin nc ta.  l s vn ng khch quan ph hp vi cch mng nc ta; ng thi, phn nh cng lao tri bin ca ng, ca Ch tch H Ch Minh v cng knh yu - Ngi  sng lp v rn luyn t chc on. c B Chnh tr Ban chp hnh Trung ng ng v Bc H cho php, theo  ngh ca Trung ng on thanh nin Lao ng Vit Nam, i hi ton quc ln th 3 hp t ngy 22 - 25/3/1961  quyt nh ly ngy 26/3/1931 (mt ngy trong thi gian cui ca Hi ngh Trung ng ng ln th 2, dnh  bn bc v quyt nh nhng vn  rt quan trng i vi cng tc thanh nin) lm ngy thnh lp on hng nm. Ngy 26/3 tr thnh ngy v vang ca tui tr Vit Nam, ca on Thanh nin cng sn H Ch Minh quang vinh.</span></div>\r\n<div style="margin: 6pt 0cm 0pt; line-height: 150%; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Arial;">T ngy 26/3/1931 n nay,  ph hp vi yu cu nhim v ca tng thi k cch mng, on  i tn nhiu ln:</span></div>\r\n<div style="margin: 6pt 0cm 0pt; line-height: 150%; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Arial;">- T 1931 - 1936: on TNCS Vit Nam, on TNCS ng Dng</span></div>\r\n<div style="margin: 6pt 0cm 0pt; line-height: 150%; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Arial;">- T 1937 - 1939: on Thanh nin Dn ch ng Dng</span></div>\r\n<div style="margin: 6pt 0cm 0pt; line-height: 150%; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Arial;">- T 11/1939 - 1941: on Thanh nin phn  ng Dng</span></div>\r\n<div style="margin: 6pt 0cm 0pt; line-height: 150%; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Arial;">- T 5/1941 - 1956: on Thanh nin cu quc Vit Nam</span></div>\r\n<div style="margin: 6pt 0cm 0pt; line-height: 150%; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Arial;">- T 25/10/1956 - 1970: on Thanh nin Lao ng Vit Nam</span></div>\r\n<div style="margin: 6pt 0cm 0pt; line-height: 150%; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Arial;">- T 2/1970 - 11/1976: on Thanh nin lao ng H Ch Minh</span></div>\r\n<div style="margin: 6pt 0cm 0pt; line-height: 150%; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Arial;">- T 12/1976 n nay: on Thanh nin cng sn H Ch Minh</span></div>\r\n<div style="margin: 6pt 0cm 0pt; line-height: 150%; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: Arial;">Nhng th h thanh nin k tip nhau  chin u anh dng v c lp t do ca T Quc, v ch ngha x hi  lin tip lp nn nhng chin cng xut sc v trng thnh vt bc. </span></div>\r\n</span></span></span>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>', '', 1, 1, 0, 5, '2011-12-22 18:43:42', 62, '', '2011-12-22 18:45:14', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:0