(97, 'Trng Ngn ng Tokyo Nakano(Tokyo Nakano Language School)', 'trng-ngon-ng-tokyo-nakanotokyo-nakano-language-school', '', '<p><span style="font-size: 8pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 8pt;" face="Arial" size="2">Trng Ngn ng Tokyo Nakano c thnh lp t thng 01 nm 2002,  c ph duyt bi Hip hi Xc tin Gio dc Ngn ng Nht Bn</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 8pt;" face="Arial" size="2">&nbsp;Vi i ng gio vin tr, nhng ngi  nghin cu ging dy trn khp cc trng i hc v sau i hc nn c nhiu kinh nghim phong ph trong vic ging dy ting Nht cng nh trong vic hng dn hc sinh  gip nc ch nh Nht Bn.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 8pt;" face="Arial" size="2">L mt trng thch hp vi xu hng ton cu nh hin nay, Tokyo Nakano Language School nhm mc ch a ra cc c hi  hp tc vi cc quc gia khc nhau v hiu nhau  chia s nhn thc i vi th gii hin i khng ch c thng qua gio dc ting Nht m cn thng qua gio dc ton din vi cc ro cn gia cc quc gia v nn vn ha.Nh trng tin rng n l cn thit cho Nht Bn trong tng lai v cho th gii.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 8pt;" face="Arial" size="2">ng ngn ngi tham kho  kin vi chng ti v lo lng v kh khn ca bn cng nh hc tp. Gio vin nhng ngi c th ni ting Trung v ting Anh lun lun sn sng gip  cc bn, ngay c nhng sinh vin mi va n Nht Bn khng phi lo lng.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 8pt;" face="Arial" size="2">Hy tm hiu "Nht Bn" thng qua trao i vi nhng ngi Nht Bn! Trng cng a ra cc c hi  trao i vi cc tnh nguyn vin v sinh vin cc trng i hc khc nhau, cc trng trung hc v trng trung hc c s. Cc bn s c th c c s hiu bit tt hn v "Nht Bn" thng qua hnh thc giao lu nh vy.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 8pt;" face="Arial" size="2">Hng dn cuc sng hng ngy cho hc sinh: Xin vui lng khng ngn ngi tham kho  kin vi chng ti v tt c mi th nh nhng g bn khng bit hoc gp rc ri trong cuc sng ca bn ti Nht Bn. Tt c cc nhn vin ca chng ti s tn tnh t vn cho bn. Ngoi ra, nh trng thng mi cc nhn vin cnh st trong dch v t Nakano  cung cp hng dn cuc sng hng ngy cho hc sinh mi nhp hc. <br /> </span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><strong><span style="font-family: Arial;" face="Arial" size="2">Lch hc v gi hc</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<table style="width: 295px; border-collapse: collapse;" border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr style="height: 17.1pt;">\r\n<td style="width: 0.95in; border: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0in 5.4pt; height: 17.1pt;" rowspan="2" valign="top" width="91">\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 8pt;" face="Arial" size="2">Thi gian ln lp</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="width: 69.15pt; border-width: 1pt 1pt 1pt medium; border-style: solid solid solid none; border-color: windowtext windowtext windowtext -moz-use-text-color; padding: 0in 5.4pt; height: 17.1pt;" valign="top" width="92">\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 8pt;" face="Arial" size="2">Bui sng</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="width: 84pt; border-width: 1pt 1pt 1pt medium; border-style: solid solid solid none; border-color: windowtext windowtext windowtext -moz-use-text-color; padding: 0in 5.4pt; height: 17.1pt;" valign="top" width="112">\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 8pt;" face="Arial" size="2">9:00 ~ 12:50</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style="height: 9.1pt;">\r\n<td style="width: 69.15pt; border-width: medium 1pt 1pt medium; border-style: none solid solid none; border-color: -moz-use-text-color windowtext windowtext -moz-use-text-color; padding: 0in 5.4pt; height: 9.1pt;" valign="top" width="92">\r\n<p><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 8pt;" face="Arial" size="2">Bui chiu</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="width: 84pt; border-width: medium 