(72, '10 gng mt xut sc nhn gii thng Qu cu vng', '10-gng-mt-xut-sc-nhn-gii-thng-qu-cu-vang', '', '<p style="text-align: justify;">Web.TN: Chiu ngy (15/12), ti H Ni, Hi ng chung tuyn gii thng khoa hc k thut thanh nin Qu cu vng 2011  chn c 10 gng mt t 68 h s cc ti nng tr xut sc gi v  trao gii thng Qu cu vng 2011, xp theo cc lnh vc gm: cng ngh thng tin - truyn thng v cng ngh y - dc mi lnh vc 3 c nhn, cng ngh sinh hc, cng ngh mi trng mi lnh vc 2 c nhn.</p>\r\n<div class="body_description">\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: 12px;"><br /></span></span></div>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: 12px;">Theo nh gi ca ban t chc, 10 gng mt nhn gii thng l nhng ti nng  t thnh tch xut sc trong qu trnh hc tp, cng tc,  c cc gii php sng to, cc cng trnh nghin cu, gii php k thut ni bt, c gi tr khoa hc cao hoc c  ngha thc tin ln, mang li hiu qu kinh t, x hi c bit ti a phng, n v ng dng. </span></span></div>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;"></div>\r\n<table style="width: 400px;" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src="http://doanthanhnien.vn/Uploads/634286312229367500.jpg" alt="nh minh ha" height="282" hspace="5" vspace="5" width="400" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="middle" align="center"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: 12px;"><span style="color: #0000ff;">nh minh ha</span></span></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial;" class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial">Gii thng Qu Cu Vng l hot ng do Trung ng on v B KHCN ch tr t chc t nm 2003, cho n nm 2010 ch xt trao cho cc ti nng tr trong lnh vc CNTT. Trc thc tin pht trin mnh m v vai tr quan trng ca cc lnh vc khoa hc, cng ngh khc, t nm 2011 gii thng c m rng thnh Gii thng KHKT Thanh nin, xt trao cho cc ti nng tr (khng qu 35 tui) tiu biu trong 4 lnh vc: Cng ngh thng tin v truyn thng; Cng ngh y  dc; Cng ngh sinh hc; Cng ngh mi trng. <strong></strong></span></div>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial;" class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial"><strong>Phn thng cho mi ti nng tr ot gii l 40 triu ng, c trao vo cui thng 12.2011</strong>.&nbsp;<span style="font-family: Arial;" class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial"> </span></span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style="text-align: right;" class="news_author"><strong>(Theo on Thanh Nin)</strong></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '', 1, 3, 0, 21, '2011-12-18 05:15:47', 62, '', '2011-12-22 18:22:55', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-12-18 05:12:25', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 3, 0, 2, '', '', 0, 32, 'robots=\nauthor=');
