(61, 'Gio dc gip hc sinh hnh thnh h gi tr ca bn thn', 'giao-dc-giup-hc-sinh-hinh-thanh-h-gia-tr-ca-bn-than', '', '<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Nh trng gip ngi hc hnh thnh v pht trin h gi tr ca tng ngi: tm lc, tr lc, th lc- gi tr hc thc, gi tr sng, gi tr tay ngh v lng tm ngh, gi tr ng gp..., gi tr t khng nh mnh...</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Nguyn B trng B GD-T GS.VS Phm Minh Hc- Ch tch Hi Cu gio chc Vit Nam  pht biu v Trit l gio dc hin nay ti bui ta m "trit l gio dc Vit Nam" do Bo in t CSVN t chc hm 31/8 ti H Ni.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table class="image center" style="width: 484px;" align="center" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img alt="Bui ta m sng nay do bo in t ng Cng sn t chc sng nay." src="http://www.gdtd.vn/dataimages/201109/original/images565401_2.jpg" height="320" width="484" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="image_desc" align="center">Bui ta m sng nay do bo in t ng Cng sn t chc. nh: gdtd.vn</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">GS.TS Phng Hu Ph- Ph Ch tch thng trc Hi ng L lun T, Ch tch Hi ng khoa hc cc c quan ng T  d v c nhng  kin ng gp qu bu trong bui ta m.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">GS.Phm Minh Hc cho rng, trit l gio dc nc nh  c t xa xa. ng ly mc lch s khi c Quc t gim (1076) n th k th 19. Theo ng, trit l gio dc Vit Nam trong lch s  c th hin su sc trong t tng ca cc bc hin trit tiu biu tng thi k, ca cc nh vn ha- gio dc tiu biu: Chu Vn An (TK 14), H Qu Ly, Nguyn Tri (cui TK 14, u TK15), L Thnh Tng (TK 15), L Qu n, La Sn Phu T Nguyn Thip, Ng Thi Nhm (TK 18), Nguyn Trng T (TK 19).&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">GS Phm Minh Hc nhn nh: Sut 843 nm (1076-1919), ti Vit Nam song song tn ti hai dng gio dc chnh thng (h thng gio dc t chng, khoa c, quan trng) v khng chnh thng th hin qua t tng, quan nim v gio dc ca cc thy  Nho, dy hc trong dn gian, dy hc tr l con em cc gia nh truyn thng trong cc lng Vit xa c ghi nhn trong vn vn hc dn gian (ca dao, tc ng). Hp lu nhng g tinh tu, tch cc ca hai dng gio dc chnh thng v gio dc dn gian  to lp nn trit l gio dc Vit Nam trong lch s, th hin :  thc dn tc; Tinh thn hiu hc; Trit l nhn sinh Tnh Ngha; Gi tr gia nh; Kt cu x hi bn vng: nh- lng- nc.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Thi k tip sau &nbsp;(TK 20) l bc ngot ln nh hng n nn gio dc nc nh cng nh trit l gio dc thi by gi. Cc ch s yu nc tiu biu cho thi k  phi k n Phan Bi Chu, Phan Chu Trinh v cc phong tro ng du, ng kinh ngha thc v Truyn b quc ng. Thng qua cc hot ng ca mnh, cc nh ch s ny  a trit l gio dc thnh tinh thn yu nc.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">K tip l t tng gio dc v i H Ch Minh. T tng "chng gic dt" ca Ngi c th hin rt sm trong thi k ch  h. Ngay sau khi Cch mng Thng 8 thnh cng, vic u tin Ngi ngh n l nc Vit Nam mi ginh c c lp phi dit c "gic dt".&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table class="image leftside" style="width: 250px;" align="left" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img alt="GS.VS Phm Minh Hc" src="http://www.gdtd.vn/dataimages/201109/original/images565404_1.jpg" height="219" width="250" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="image_desc" align="center">GS.VS Phm Minh Hc</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">GS Phm Minh Hc vin dn, v gio dc, Bc H  tng vit: "dy lm sao phi dy thnh ngi" v "ngi Vit Nam mun hc phi hc Khng T, mun lm Cch mng phi hc L- nin"; Bc  tng cn dn cc thy c gio: "D kh khn n u cng phi thi ua dy tt v hc tt".... m xut pht t t tng, trit l gio dc  ca Ngi, ngnh gio dc  c nhiu cuc vn ng, phoing tro thi ua, tiu biu nh "Hai tt".&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">T trit l gio dc Vit Nam trong lch s n trit l gio dc Cch mng (t thng 8/1945): Trit l gio dc H Ch Minh (k c qua cc vn kin ca ng CSVN), trit l gio dc Dn ch nhn dn, trit l gio dc Khng chin kin quc, trit l gio dc thi i mi (n i hi XI): kinh t th trng nh hng XHCN, hi nhp, ton cu ho... c th gp phn khng nh t trc ti nay Vit nam c trit l gio dc (t tng,  tng v gio dc c th nghim, tri nghim, c rt thnh kinh nghim sng, ri li em ra thc hnh...)&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">GS Phm Minh Hc khng nh: trit l gio dc c  nhiu tng bc: tng con ngi, gia nh, trng lp, quc gia.  phm vi quc gia  l ng li, ch trng, chnh sch, chin lc, k hoch pht trin gio dc  thnh tu 66 nm pht trin gio dc nc nh l minh chng rt r.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Thc t cuc sng i hi l lun gio dc ca chng ta phi c pht trin mi, gp phn trin khai ch trng, chnh sch pht trin GD-T trong thi k mi.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">GS Phm Minh Hc  xut trit l gio dc l: gio dc h gi tr bn thn:&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Nh trng hnh thnh v pht trin  ngi hc h gi tr ca tng ngi: tm lc, tr lc, th lc  gi tr hc thc, gi tr sng, gi tr tay ngh v lng tm ngh, gi tr ng gp..., gi tr t khng nh mnh;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Ngi hc to cho mnh c cc gi tr  sng v hot ng, pht huy h gi tr bn thn em li cuc sng cho mnh, gia nh v cng ng, x hi;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">X hi (bao gm c Nh nc) to mi trng thun li (bao gm cc chnh sch, thi  ng x, nht l tn trng gi tr ca tng ngi) cho mi ngi hnh thnh, pht trin, pht huy cc gi tr bn thn.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">GS, TS Trn Ngc Hin- Nguyn Ph G Hc vin Chnh tr quc gia H Ch Minh cho rng: nhu cu i mi cn bn v ton din nn gio dc, o to  nc ta  tr nn cp bch. V vy, i mi nn gio dc khng n gin a ra mt chng trnh m trc ht cn lm r chng ta i mi gio dc&nbsp;trong khng gian v thi gian no v kinh t, x hi - vn ho v chnh tr t ra i vi gio dc, o to. Trc ht cn t s nghip gio dc, o to trong qu trnh chuyn i m hnh pht trin ca t nc v mc ch trc tip ca gio dc, o to l to ra ngun lc lao ng v qun l ph hp vi yu cu ca qu trnh pht trin, nh  m nng cao dn tr theo mi bc i.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">V nh hng, GS Trn Ngc Hin cho rng: phi nh hng cho ng v nh hng s chi phi ni dung chng trnh, cch t chc nn gio dc, phng php dy v hc.  nh hng pht trin nn gio dc nc ta nh l s tch hp nhng gi tr ca thi i mi ang hnh thnh vi nhng gi tr tt p ca vn ho Vit Nam.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Theo ng: cn gio dc t duy c lp - nhn t  pht trin ton din ca mi c nhn; kt hp hi ho tri thc khoa hc k thut vi tri thc khoa hc x hi - nhn vn l nh hng nn gio dc mi, v xy dng mi trng vn ho trong hot ng gio dc, o to, nhng iu tt p c truyn cho th h tr, ch yu l thng qua quan h trc tip vi ngi thy v c ngi qun l gio dc, ch khng phi ch yu qua sch v. Chnh mi quan h y to ra mi trng vn ho trong gio dc...&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">GS. TS Phm Tt Dong- Ph Ch tch Hi khuyn hc Vit Nam: cho rng: Hin ti l nguyn kh quc gia; hc tp l gc r ca gio ha, phng ngn  vn cn nguyn tnh thi s i vi ngnh GD-T hin nay. Mt quc gia khng c ngi hin ti s l mt quc gia ng trc nhng b tc trong bi ton pht trin. Vy nn, theo ng, cn phi c trit l gio dc trong iu kin xy dng nn gio dc tri thc. Do vy, mun lm tt, cn thc hin tt li dy ca H Ch Minh: Hc khng bao gi cng. Hc mi  tin b mi. Cng tin b cng thy cn phi hc thm.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">GS.TS Phm Mnh Hng - Nguyn Ph Trng ban Ban Khoa gio T  cp vn  ham hc, lm sao  ton dn ham hc, ng lc ham hc  y thc s l thi ua ch khng phi l ganh ua.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">GS.TS V Minh Giang  Ph Gim c i hc quc gia H Ni nu vt thc t hn: xy dng trit l gio dc bt u t u. Vit Nam  c nhng iu kin g. Trit l gio dc Vit Nam phi bao gm nhng yu cu g. Theo&nbsp;ng:&nbsp;vic xy dng trit l gio dc Vit Nam phi&nbsp; hiu c 5 vn ,  l: Hiu con ngi Vit Nam; Hiu lch s gio dc ca t nc; Hiu xu th th gii; Hiu nhng yu cu ca t nc, ng, nhn dn vi gio dc; Hiu c nhng yu t tc ng ti gio dc Vit Nam.</p>\r\n<p>Pht biu kt lun bui ta m, ng ch Phng Hu Ph nh gi cao sng kin ca Bo TDCS  t chc bui ta m rt cn thit v thit thc ny.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Mc ch ca bui ta m hm nay  thy c nhng gi tr, nhng tinh hoa ca dn tc ta v trit l gio dc  tip tc vn dng, cn nhc hon cnh lch s hin nay, tnh hnh kinh t, x hi, vn ha hin nay  hnh thnh trit l gio dc Vit Nam ng, c sc sng v c tnh kh thi.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Trong qu trnh trin khai sp ti, bn cnh vic xy dng kt hoch, quy hoch cc chng trnh  n c th, chin lc gio dc Vit Nam 2011 - 2020 cn hnh thnh c mt trit l gio dc v truyn b su rng trit l gio dc trong thy, tr, cng ng x hi, coi y l mt b phn quan trng khng th tch ri trong chin lc i mi gio dc trong 10 nm ti.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><strong>GD&amp;T</strong></p>', '', 1, 1, 0, 4, '2011-12-13 07:55:48', 62, '', '2011-12-22 17:31:10', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-12-13 07:55:18', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 4, 0, 1, '', '', 0, 21, 'robots=\nauthor='),
