: 0cm 5.4pt;" valign="top" width="113"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;Thc s<br /></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><em><span style="text-decoration: underline;">II, Nhng cng vic nhm trng ph trch</span></em></span></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><em><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><span style="text-decoration: none;">&nbsp;</span></span></em>1. Lp k hoch hot ng ni, ngoi kha nm hc</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"> &nbsp;2. Lp k hoch ging dy 3 khi theo nm hc</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"> &nbsp;3. Phn cng cc thnh vin ph trch theo chuyn mn</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"> &nbsp;4. Bao qut chung v chu trch nhim mi hot ng ca nhm</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"> &nbsp;5. Thng k cc hc sinh c nng khiu v mn th thao</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 33px; text-indent: -0.5in; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 6. Bi dng tp luyn t chc thi u hi khe Ph ng cp trng, cp&nbsp;&nbsp; qun &nbsp;theo nm hc</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"> &nbsp;7. Bm st v theo di lch thi u cp thnh ph&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"> &nbsp;8. Kim tra h s CM cc thnh vin trong nhm</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"> &nbsp;9. D gi thm lp nh gi chuyn mn</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"> 10. Cp nht thng tin ca trng, thng bo cho cc thnh vin trong nhm</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"> 11. Ghi chp thng tin v sinh hot chuyn mn ca nhm</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"> 12. T chc sinh hot chuyn </span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"> 13. Qun l trong thit b gio dc</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"> 14. Ra  kim tra khi 10,11,12 ( thng nht cng trong nhm  biu bng chm)</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"> 15. Ph trch qun l v bi dng tp luyn, thi u cu lc b khiu v, c vua, c tng, bi li.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><br /></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><strong><em>III, Nhng vic lm ca cc thnh vin</em></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>1, ng ch Ng Vit Hon</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">- Lp k hoch ging dy c nhn theo nm hc</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">- Chu trch nhim 6 mn thi u cp thnh ph, cp qun: v, bng bn,  cu, cu lng, ko co, bng .</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2, ng ch Nguyn Th Phng<br /></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">- Lp k hoch ging dy theo nm hc.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">- Chu trch nhim v ph trch 4 mn thi u cp qun v cp thnh ph: bng r, ko co, in kinh, bng .</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">- Thc hin nhim v khi t v trng iu ng.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>3, ng ch Phm S Huy</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">- Lp k hoch ging dy c nhn theo nm hc</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">- Chu trch nhim v ph trch mn bng , in kinh.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">- Thc hin nhim v khi t v trng iu ng.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><em><span style="text-decoration: underline;">IV, Thnh tch  t c trong nm hc 2011  2012</span></em></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>1, Cp qun:</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - Gii ba bng r</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - 9 gii c nhn: in kinh, cu lng, c vua, c tng.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - 2 Gii nht ko co, bng bn.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>2, Cp thnh ph:</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - 1 gii huy chng ng ng i mn khiu v.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - 2 gii ca nhn huy chng ng mn khiu v.</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 60px; text-align: right;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; H ni, ngy 27/3/2012</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 219px; text-indent: 27pt; text-align: right;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><strong>Ngi vit: V Th Quyn</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 219px; text-indent: 27pt; text-align: right;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><strong><br /></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="margin-left: 219px; text-indent: 27pt; text-align: right;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><strong><br /></strong></span></p>', 1, 1, 0, 6, '2012-03-27 02:11:13', 80, '', '2012-04-08 08:47:02', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-03-27 02:04:26', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 12, 0, 1, '', '', 0, 17, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(64, 'Thi HSG quc gia nm 2012 s c mt s im mi', 'thi-hsg-quc-gia-nm-2012-s-co-mt-s-im-mi', '', '<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>B GD&amp;T va ban hnh hng dn t chc k thi chn HSG quc gia THPT nm 2012. </strong></p>\r\n<table style="width: 100%;" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p class="storyInlinePhoto"><img src="http://giaoducthoidai.vn/dataimages/201112/original/images605057_1.jpg" width="95%" /></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>Theo hng dn ny, t nm 2012, cng vi vic thc hin hnh thc thi vit v thi lp trnh trn my vi tnh, B GD&amp;T s tng bc trin khai thc hin hnh thc thi ni i vi cc mn Ngoi ng v hnh thc thi thc hnh i vi cc mn Vt l, Ha hc, Sinh hc. Bc u, trong k thi HSG nm 2012, cc mn Ngoi ng s c thm hnh thc thi ni  mc c thoi ca th sinh; i vi cc mn Vt l, Ha hc, Sinh hc, s c cu hi v thc hnh trong  thi.<br /> <br /> Phm vi ni dung thi s nm chng trnh gio dc THPT hin hnh v chng trnh chuyn su cc mn chuyn cp THPT. Thi gian thi trong hai ngy 11 v 12/1/2012.<br /> <br /> B GD&amp;T cng cng b quy nh ring i vi thi ni mn Ngoi ng, trong  c quy trnh thc hin phn thi ca th sinh.<br /> <br /> C th, sau khi vo phng thi, th sinh bc thm  thi, nhn giy nhp t gim th trong phng thi, s dng tn truy cp v mt khu do gim th trong phng thi cp  ng nhp vo trang thi. ng nhp thnh cng vo trang thi, th sinh s kch chut vo  Vo thi  hin th ca s bi thi. Sau , th sinh phi ngay lp tc kch chut tri vo  Allow (nu khng bi thi ca th sinh s b v hiu), ri chun b cu tr li cho cu hi trong bi thi. Th sinh s bt u tr li khi h thng bo bt u ghi m.<br /> <br /> H thng s t ng ngng ghi m khi ht thi gian tr li cho php. Khi trn mn hnh my hin th ch  gi ln server. Bn  hon thnh tr li cu hi, th sinh kch chut vo  ti v  lu file ghi m vo th mc do gim th to sn, tip theo kch vo  np bi  kt thc phn thi; sau , kch chut tri vo  thot  thot ra khi ti khon thi. Cui cng, th sinh cng gim th trong phng thi kim tra file ghi m  lu trn my tnh v k xc nhn ln a CD ghi file .<br /> <br /> Lu , khi h thng bt u ghi m, th sinh phi c m s ca  thi, ni dung cu cu hi trong  thi trc khi bt u tr li, trng hp ngc li, phn tr li ca th sinh b coi l phm quy. Th sinh khng c  cp n cc thng tin c nhn trong phn tr li, khng c to ra cc ting ng nhm nh du phn thi ca mnh. Gim th trong phng thi cng khng c to ra ting ng l khi h thng ang ghi m phn tr li ca th sinh.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><strong>GD&amp;T</strong></p>', '', 1, 2, 0, 15, '2011-12-13 07:58:59', 62, '', '2011-12-22 18:01:54', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-12-13 07:58:02', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 2, 0, 2, '', '', 0, 35, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(66, 'Hng ti mt trit l dy vn', 'hng-ti-mt-trit-ly-dy-vn', '', '<p style="text-align: justify;">TTCT - Dy vn gp phn tch cc nht, hiu qu nht v su sc trong qu trnh hnh thnh nhn cch con ngi...</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="pBody">&nbsp;C mt giai thoi xa th v k v mt k thi v tranh theo ch  trng: c hai tc phm ng lu  v c vn . Bc tranh th nht v mt trng trn vnh vnh, r rng; bc th hai khng thy trng u c, ch c m my rc sng.<img style="float: right;" src="data/giaoduc/demo/slide/photo04.jpg" alt="" height="187" width="249" /></p>\r\n<p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;">Gim kho A chm bc th nht im 10; bc th hai im 0 (v lc ). Gim kho B chm bc th nht 5 im (im trung bnh); bc th hai 10 im (im tuyt i) v gii thch y mi l bc tranh ngh thut ch thc, y sng to, c v theo th php dng vn ha nguyt (ly my v trng).</p>\r\n<p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;">D nhin chm thi th phi c p n. Nhng ch bit c p n m qun mt thc t bi lm ca th sinh th c khc g ngi i sa giy ch tin vo ci ni chn ca mnh! Hung chi ci ni d l l tng my cng ch l mt kiu ging Procuste m thi (trong thn thoi phng Ty, nhn vt Procuste c mt ci ging; khi bt c ai Procuste o ngi  bng ci ging ca mnh.</p>\r\n', '\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;">Ai va vn th c tha; ai qu kh th cht bt; ai ngn hn th b ko ra)! T thc t chm thi, ti cm thy lo lng t nhiu chng ta vn dng p n nh mt kiu ging Procuste.</p>\r\n<p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;">Bao lu nay, chng ta tri buc mnh mt cch nghit ng trong nhng yu cu c tnh nguyn tc v cht php lnh: gio n, p n, t l hc sinh ln lp, hc sinh thi u, t l hc sinh gii... Qun quanh v lng tng trong nhng chic vng kim c y v chng ta khng c mt trit l dy vn.</p>\r\n<p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;">Cn thit c mt trit l gio dc hon chnh  hnh thnh mt trit l dy vn thch ng. Trong lch s gio dc ca th gii, tng c thi i mun o to nhng con ngi khng l, bch khoa, tng c thi mun o to nhng ngi qun t, nhng k trng phu. Nu nn gio dc VN hm nay mun o to nhng con ngi VN sng to  mi lnh vc th chng ta phi c mt trit l dy vn ng nh bn cht sng to ca loi hnh ny.</p>\r\n<p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;">Tim nng sng to ca hc sinh c nui dng, c kch thch, c to iu kin pht trin v th thch t nh n ln nh mt h thng s  ra nhng con ngi sng to. ng ngh tnh thm m v cht sng to ca vn hc ch kch thch, nui dng s sng to trong phm vi ngh thut. Hn ai ht, nhng nh khoa hc ln lun lun khng nh ngh thut v khoa hc l i cnh ca nhn loi.</p>\r\n<p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;">A. Einstein  tng tuyn b rng thuyt tng i ca ng c gi  t nhng trang tiu thuyt su thm ca Dostoievsky. V sau khi  tin s vt l, nh khoa hc v i v l i ny  n thm thy gio dy vn hi ng hc trung hc!</p>\r\n<p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;">Nu mun o to nhng con ngi sng to th chng ta phi c mt trit l dy vn dnh cho nhng ch th. iu ny phi ni Nht Bn l quc gia u tin  chu   lm c. Hin nay  hc ng VN, ngi thy c xu hng l nhng cng chc, cn hc sinh l nhng khch th. V vy, chng ta b qun tim nng sng to v tn ca ngi dy hc v ca hc sinh, sinh vin.</p>\r\n<p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;">Nhng trit l gio dc v trit l dy vn khng ch c nh th. Chng no x hi chng ta cn c nhng bc s la o bnh nhn, nhng thy thuc mn vic cha bnh  cht p, nhng quan chc tham ... chng ta vn cn suy ngh v trit l dy hc m nng nht l trit l dy vn.</p>\r\n<p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;">Chng no x hi chng ta cn c nhng hin tng ngi khim th phi ln ting ti l k khuyt tt, xin ng thu tin v xe but ca ti, chng ta vn cn phi b sung trit l dy vn. Chng no cn c nhng sinh vin ch v  khi tr s n 2 triu ng m ra tay git ngi bn gi cho mnh vay tin, chng ta vn cn lo ngh v mt trit l dy vn.</p>\r\n<p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;">Bi v vic dy vn gp phn tch cc nht, hiu qu nht v su sc trong qu trnh hnh thnh nhn cch con ngi.</p>\r\n<p class="pBody" style="text-align: right;"><strong>Theo Tui tr online</strong></p>', 1, 3, 0, 20, '2011-12-13 08:01:02', 62, '', '2011-12-22 18:02:45', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-12-13 08:00:11', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 12, 0, 2, '', '', 0, 53, 'robots=\nauthor=');
