(68, 'Lc thng tin du hc', 'lc-thong-tin-du-hc', '', '<p class="pHead" style="text-align: justify;">TT - Hng lot trin lm du hc t cp ph thng n i hc, sau i hc c t chc. Gia mt rng thng tin du hc, hc sinh, sinh vin, ph huynh cn trang b mt s kinh nghim  tm ng thng tin du hc ang cn.</p>\r\n<table class="tLegend" style="border-collapse: separate; width: 40px;" align="center" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="2">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="text-align: justify;"><img alt="cjhsdkjdsks ksdjhkjshl " class="lImage" src="http://images1.tuoitre.vn/tianyon/ImageView.aspx?ThumbnailID=529644" style="border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px;" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="text-align: justify;">Theo cc nh t vn, ngi tham gia trin lm du hc cn tm hiu tht k thng tin du hc t i din tuyn sinh ca cc trng - nh: NH HNG</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;">Mt thc t nhiu hc sinh, sinh vin khi tham d trin lm du hc thng khng nm c thng tin v trng, loi hnh o to, ch  chnh sch vi du hc sinh quc t, iu kin n ... khin vic tm thng tin ti trin lm du hc nh ci nga xem hoa, ph cng sc, thi gian nhng khng t c kt qu.</p>\r\n', '\r\n<p class="pInterTitle" style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Ch ng tm kim</strong></p>\r\n<p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;">ng Nguyn Trng Giang, chuyn vin t vn Cng ty t vn du hc quc t CMI Vit Nam (Q.Tn Bnh, TP.HCM), chia s: Hc sinh, sinh vin d nh du hc ti quc gia no nn vo cc website ca lnh s qun, quc gia, trng...  nm ngay thng tin v nn gio dc ca nc , trong  cn ch  ti cc quy nh, chnh sch ca chnh ph i vi du hc sinh. Sau , phi ch ng tm hiu thng tin v ngnh ngh, trng, hc ph, iu kin n , lm thm... t cc ngun thng tin chnh thng hoc cc cng ty t vn du hc c uy tn, cht lng v c cc lnh s qun, cc c quan gio dc cng nhn.</p>\r\n<p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;">B Phm Th Thng Long, chuyn vin t vn Cng ty du hc Th H Mi (Q.1, TP.HCM), khuyn trc khi n d trin lm, ngi tham d nn xem k danh sch cc trng tham gia trin lm chun b sn danh sch cc trng mun gp. Ngoi ra, ngi tham d trin lm cn tm hiu xem bng cp, kinh nghim c cho php bn hi  iu kin nhp hc ca trng d nh du hc, v nn tham vn v s tng thch gia h thng vn bng  Vit Nam v quc gia chn du hc.</p>\r\n<p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;">Nhiu hc sinh, sinh vin coi cc trin lm du hc l dp  sn cc sut hc bng du hc bn phn, ton phn. L Anh, trng tuyn chng trnh hc bng Chnh ph Singapore, du hc sinh HQG Singapore, bt m: i din tuyn sinh ca cc trng khi t chc trin lm u c 1-2 sut hc bng bn phn hoc ton phn dnh cho hc sinh, sinh vin n tham d trin lm.  chp ly c hi ginh cc sut hc bng ny, hc sinh, sinh vin tham d cn chun b trc mt b h s bng ting Anh gm bi lun vit v bn thn, th gii thiu, bn thnh tch hc tp, cc giy chng nhn cc hot ng x hi....</p>\r\n<p class="pInterTitle" style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Hi ci mnh cn</strong></p>\r\n<p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;">Khi n tham d trin lm du hc, vic lit k ra giy cc cu hi lin quan n vic chn trng, kha hc... sau  tng hp thnh mt danh sch cc cu hi l iu ngi tham d nn lm. L Th Mai Phng, cu du hc sinh Trng H Kent State (M), bt m: Ngi tham d thc mc vn  g hy ch ng, mnh dn hi i din tuyn sinh ca cc trng. Cu hi cng chi tit s gip bn hnh dung cuc sng du hc ca mnh  nc ngoi. Vo cui bui trin lm, bn c th n tr chuyn thn mt vi i din tuyn sinh ca cc trng  trao i thm cc thng tin khc v cuc sng, con ngi...  quc gia d nh i du hc.</p>\r\n<p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;">Theo anh Nguyn Thi, chuyn vin t vn Cng ty du hc Vietint (Q.1), hc sinh, sinh vin, ph huynh n d trin lm khng nn ly tt c cc ti liu c sn trn quy, m ch nn thu thp nhng thng tin thch hp. Khi chn c trng ng k i du hc, ngi tham d ch nn thu thp tt c cc thng tin lin quan n trng d nh du hc. Ngoi ra, nu s trng bn chn vt qu hai, bn cn so snh v hc ph, chng trnh o to, iu kin n , xp hng trng...  tm hiu thng tin.</p>\r\n<p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;">Khi i du hc t tc, khu chng minh ti chnh l cc k quan trng. Nu hc sinh, sinh vin khng chng minh c bn thn c kh nng t tc ti chnh gm: hc ph, n , sinh hot, mua sch v, di chuyn... s b nh rt visa ngay. V th ch Phm Th Dung, chuyn vin t vn Cng ty t vn du hc L&amp;V (Q.3), cho bit: Khi trao i vi i din tuyn sinh ca cc trng, bn cn trnh by c th, r rng v iu kin ti chnh, nhng kh khn, vng mc v tnh hnh ti chnh ca bn thn, gia nh  nhn c nhng li khuyn ng nht.</p>\r\n<p class="pInterTitle" style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Tnh to trc hc bng bn phn</strong></p>\r\n<p class="pBody" style="text-align: justify;">Vic cc trng t chc trin lm thng bo trao tng cc sut hc bng bn phn t 20-90% hc ph ch l chiu  thuyt phc bn quyt nh i du hc. Khi du hc ti nc ngoi, hc ph ch l mt phn nh, chi ph sinh hot, n , i li, mua sch v, bo him... mi l iu ng lo ngi. V vy, khi bt ng nhn c cc sut hc bng ny, ngi tham d cn tnh to, phi tm hiu k cc khon chi ph ngoi hc ph, nu vt qu kh nng ca gia nh, bn thn th nn t b  tm kim cc c hi khc.</p>\r\n<p class="pBody" style="text-align: right;"><strong>(S/T)</strong></p>', 1, 4, 0, 26, '2011-12-13 08:04:02', 62, '', '2011-12-22 18:05:15', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-12-13 08:03:12', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 5, 0, 1, '', '', 0, 43, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(69, 'Thi tt nghip THPT: B thi cm, chm cho t 2012', 'thi-tt-nghip-thpt-b-thi-cm-chm-cheo-t-2012', '', '<p class="summary" style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	B GDT s giao quyn ch ng cho Gi&aacute;m c S GDT a phng quyt nh vic th&agrave;nh lp c&aacute;c hi ng coi thi, chm thi.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	Ng&agrave;y 12.12, B GDT c&ocirc;ng b d tho Th&ocirc;ng t v vic sa i b sung mt s iu ca quy ch thi tt nghip THPT.</p>\r\n<p class="summary" style="text-align: right;">\r\n	<img alt="" src="data/giaoduc/demo/slide/photo04.jpg" style="width: 132px; height: 100px;" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	Theo &oacute;, bt u t k thi tt nghip THPT nm 2012, B s ch&iacute;nh thc b h&igrave;nh thc thi theo cm v&agrave; chm ch&eacute;o b&agrave;i thi t lun gia c&aacute;c trng. Thay v&agrave;o &oacute;, B s giao quyn ch ng cho Gi&aacute;m c S GDT a phng quyt nh vic th&agrave;nh lp c&aacute;c hi ng coi thi, chm thi, mi hi ng gm mt hoc nhiu trng ph th&ocirc;ng, mi m&ocirc;n t lun c&oacute; 2 t chm thi, m bo gi&aacute;o vi&ecirc;n kh&ocirc;ng chm b&agrave;i thi t lun ca hc sinh trng m&igrave;nh ging dy. C&aacute;c hi ng coi thi b&agrave;n giao trc tip cho hi ng chm thi kh&ocirc;ng qua s GDT</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	Ngo&agrave;i ra, B cng b thanh tra y quyn ca B trong k thi, gi&aacute;m c c&aacute;c s t th&agrave;nh lp c&aacute;c o&agrave;n thanh tra, trong &oacute; c&oacute; th tng cng c&aacute;n b, ging vi&ecirc;n c&aacute;c trng H, C l&agrave;m c&ocirc;ng t&aacute;c coi thi.</p>\r\n', '\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	Vic lp danh s&aacute;ch th&iacute; sinh ng k&yacute; thi cng c sa i, b sung. C th: Trong mi hi ng coi thi, danh s&aacute;ch th&iacute; sinh c sp xp theo 3 bc.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	<em>Bc 1</em>, xp theo th t ban: Th&iacute; sinh Ban Khoa hc t nhi&ecirc;n, Ban Khoa hc x&atilde; hi v&agrave; nh&acirc;n vn, Ban C bn; th&iacute; sinh gi&aacute;o dc thng xuy&ecirc;n (nu c&oacute;).</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	<em>Bc 2,</em> xp theo th t u ti&ecirc;n ca m&ocirc;n thi ngoi ng (tr th&iacute; sinh gi&aacute;o dc thng xuy&ecirc;n): Ting Anh, ting Nga, ting Ph&aacute;p, ting Trung Quc, ting c, ting Nht.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	<em>Bc 3</em>, lp danh s&aacute;ch th&iacute; sinh cho mi m&ocirc;n thi ngoi ng v&agrave; d&agrave;nh ri&ecirc;ng cho gi&aacute;o dc thng xuy&ecirc;n (nu c&oacute;) theo th t a, b, c&hellip; ca t&ecirc;n th&iacute; sinh. S b&aacute;o danh ca th&iacute; sinh c &aacute;nh t 0001 n ht s th&iacute; sinh ca hi ng coi thi.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	Quy nh mi ca B GDT kh&ocirc;ng ch khin ph huynh hc sinh &ldquo;th ph&agrave;o&rdquo; m&agrave; c&ograve;n gi&uacute;p c&aacute;c trng v&agrave; s th&aacute;o g nhiu kh&oacute; khn. H&igrave;nh thc thi cm, chm ch&eacute;o c trin khai t nm 2009, theo &oacute; mi cm thi c&oacute; &iacute;t nht 3 trng hoc 3 trung t&acirc;m gi&aacute;o dc thng xuy&ecirc;n.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	Tin h&agrave;nh c 3 nm, &ldquo;thi cm - chm ch&eacute;o&rdquo; &atilde; bc l nhng hn ch r&otilde; rt g&acirc;y kh&oacute; khn rt ln i vi hc sinh v&ugrave;ng s&acirc;u, v&ugrave;ng xa. T&igrave;nh trng c&aacute;c em phi vt n&uacute;i bng rng hoc i nhiu c&acirc;y s  n a im thi khin c th&iacute; sinh v&agrave; ph huynh mt mi. B&ecirc;n cnh &oacute;, mt s trng kh&ocirc;ng  iu kin vt cht  t chc thi theo cm cng kh&aacute; &ldquo;loay hoay&rdquo;  trin khai h&igrave;nh thc n&agrave;y.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	in h&igrave;nh, s c &ldquo;11 tnh ng bng s&ocirc;ng Cu Long c&ugrave;ng nhau tha thun n&acirc;ng im trong k thi tt nghip nm 2011&rdquo; &atilde; cho thy s thiu kh&aacute;ch quan trm trng ca h&igrave;nh thc thi n&agrave;y. Ch&iacute;nh v&igrave; vy, theo &aacute;nh gi&aacute; ca c&aacute;c chuy&ecirc;n gia gi&aacute;o dc &ldquo;h&igrave;nh thc thi cm, chm ch&eacute;o sm mun cng&hellip; ph&aacute; sn&rdquo;.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">\r\n	<strong>(D&acirc;n Vit)</strong></p>', 1, 4, 0, 25, '2011-12-17 17:00:00', 62, '', '2011-12-22 10:22:38', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-12-17 17:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 10, 0, 1, '', '', 0, 75, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(70, 'Thnh cng hm nay, nn tng ngy mai', 'thanh-cong-hom-nay-nn-tng-ngay-mai', '', '<div id="detail-content">\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>(GD&amp;T) - Ngy 17/7, Hi ngh tng kt 4 nm thc hin Ch th s 33/2006/CT-TTg, s kt 3 nm phong tro thi ua Xy dng trng hc thn thin, hc sinh tch cc v tng kt nm hc 2010-2011, trin khai nhim v nm hc 2011-2012 ti Cao Lnh, tnh ng Thp tip tc ngy&nbsp; lm vic&nbsp; th hai v  kt thc thnh cng tt p. </strong></p>\r\n<table style="width: 550px;" class="image center" align="center" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img alt="Cc lnh o S k cam kt thi ua" src="http://www.gdtd.vn/dataimages/201107/original/images549580_1.jpg" height="334" width="550" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="image_desc" align="center">Cc lnh o S k cam kt thi ua</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Trong ngy hm nay, hi ngh tip tc nhn c nhiu tham lun,  kin ng gp, chia s kinh nghim&nbsp; ca cc i biu. Trong  ng ch  l tham lun ca ng Trng Kim Minh, Gim c S GD&amp;T tnh Lo Cai; ng Nguyn nh Ban, Hiu trng Trng THCS Phan Chu Trinh, tnh k Lk&nbsp; v nhng chuyn bin vt bc ca c s sau 4 nm thc hin ch th s 33/2006/CT-TTg&nbsp; v 3 nm trin khai phong tro thi ua Xy dng trng hc thn thin, hc sinh tch cc. Cc tham lun u nhn mnh: hiu qu r nht m cuc vn ng Hai khng v phong tro thi ua Xy dng trng hc thn thin, hc sinh tch cc mang ti  l vic c x hi cng chm lo cho gio dc v o to. C h thng chnh tr vo cuc, s ng lng ca nhn dn. V  l c s  gio dc a phng chuyn bin tch cc theo hng thc cht, tng bc nng cao cht lng. V  ngha tch cc cng nh hiu qu ca cuc vn ng Hai khng v phong tro thi ua Xy dng trng hc thn thin, hc sinh tch cc, ton ngnh cn tip tc duy tr v pht trin trong thi gian ti. (Xem thm chi tit  kin cc i biu v vic thc hin ch th s 33/2006/CT-TTg&nbsp; v phong tro Xy dng trng hc thn thin, hc sinh tch cc )</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Cng trong ngy hm nay, B GD&amp;T  t chc tuyn dng khen thng nhng c nhn, tp th t thnh tch xut sc trong nm hc 2010-2011.</p>\r\n<table style="width: 550px;" class="image center" align="center" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img alt="Ph Th tng Nguyn Thin Nhn pht biu ch o ti hi ngh" src="http://www.gdtd.vn/dataimages/201107/original/images549557_2.JPG" height="413" width="550" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="image_desc" align="center">Ph Th tng Nguyn Thin Nhn pht biu ch o ti hi ngh</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">nh gi v nhng thnh tu sau mt nm hc, ng thi nhn li 4 nm trin khai cuc vn ng Hai khng, 3 nm trin khai phong tro thi ua Xy dng trng hc thn thin, hc sinh tch cc , y vin trung ng ng, Ph Th tng Chnh ph Nguyn Thin Nhn  ghi nhn v nh gi cao nhng n lc ca ton ngnh trong vic quyt lit chng tiu cc, yu km trong ngnh, tng bc nng cao cht lng gio dc theo hng thc cht v c chiu su. Ph Th tng nhn mnh: Ngnh gio dc cn phi tip tc khng ngng i mi, nng cao cht lng gio dc, thc hin mt cch trit  v thit thc cc phong tro thi ua,&nbsp; to ng lc phn u rn luyn cao hn na, mnh m hn na trong gio vin v hc sinh. Ton ngnh cn qun trit ch o ca Th tng Chnh ph Nguyn Tn Dng v su nhim v trng tm.  l i mi cng tc qun l gio dc, nng cao cht lng dy v hc; i mi v gim ti chng trnh gio dc ph thng; Chm lo cho i sng gio vin v tch cc xy dng i ng cn b qun l, nh gio; Nng cao cht lng dy v hc ngoi ng, tip tc u t v nng cao c s vt cht trng lp; Nhanh chng xy dng chin lc pht trin gio dc giai on 2011-2020.  vic i mi&nbsp; tt v hiu qu, ngnh gio dc v cc a phng cn phi xy dng c mi trng gio dc s phm tt. Trong qu trnh i mi phi bm st thc tin, lng nghe  kin t c s  cng cuc i mi mang tnh bn vng hn. Nm hc mi 2011-2012, ngnh gio dc cng phi nng cao trch nhim i vi x hi; Quyt lit thc hin i mi ton din, trong  i mi qun l l hng t ph. c bit, gio dc ph thng khng ch ch trng vic dy kin thc m cn phi tch hp vic dy kin thc vi dy k nng cho hc sinh theo hng tng cng nng lc cng dn trn bc ng hi nhp.</p>\r\n<table style="width: 500px;" class="image center" align="center" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img alt="B trng Phm V Lun pht biu ti hi ngh" src="http://www.gdtd.vn/dataimages/201107/original/images549558_1.jpg" height="375" width="500" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="image_desc" align="center">B trng Phm V Lun kt lun hi ngh</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Thay mt ton ngnh, B trng B GD&amp;T Phm V Lun pht biu tip thu  kin ch o ca Ph Th tng.&nbsp;&nbsp; B trng khng nh:&nbsp; i vi Ch th 33/2006/CT-TTg, ngnh GD&amp;T  ch ng trin khai,  c tinh thn trch nhim rt cao trc ng v nhn dn, li c thm s chia s chung tay ca cc b ngnh, lnh o cc a phng. Ngnh GD&amp;T hin nay  bt kh khn hn 4 nm trc rt nhiu, n gi ny c th khng nh mc tiu c bn ca Ch th 33/2006/CT-TTg  c thc hin mt cch hiu qu. Trn c s pht huy nhng thnh tu  t c qua 4 nm thc hin Ch th s 33/2006/CT-TTg, 3 nm trin khai phong tro thi ua Xy dng trng hc thn thin, hc sinh tch cc cng nh thnh qu ca nm hc qua, ton ngnh cn quyt tm hn na, xy dng nn gio dc trung thc lnh mnh, cht lng. Nhng mi quan h c xc lp trong ni b ngnh gio dc, gia ngnh vi cc b ngnh khc  c xc lp trong qu trnh thc hin Hai khng v Xy dng trng hc thn thin, hc sinh tch cc&nbsp; s tip tc c duy tr v pht trin. Ton ngnh quyt tm khng  ti pht tiu cc  nhng ni  chng c tiu cc v kin quyt chng ti cng  nhng&nbsp; ni cn tiu cc.</p>\r\n<table style="width: 550px;" class="image center" align="center" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><a href="http://gdtd.vn/dataimages/201107/original/images549739_1.jpg"><img alt="Ph Th tng Nguyn Thin Nhn trao bng khen cho cc tp th c thnh tch xut sc trong thc hin Ch th s 33/2006/CT-TTg" src="http://www.gdtd.vn/dataimages/201107/original/images549739_1.jpg" height="413" width="550" /></a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="image_desc" align="center">Ph Th tng Nguyn Thin Nhn trao bng khen cho cc tp th c thnh tch xut sc trong thc hin Ch th s 33/2006/CT-TTg</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Trong nhim v trin khai nm hc mi 2011-2012 ton ngnh phi&nbsp; i mi cn bn v ton din theo tinh thn Ngh quyt i hi ng ln th XI; ni dung i mi cn bn&nbsp; s c ngnh t chc nghin cu  c th ha v trin khai. Sp ti y, Chnh ph s c chng trnh hnh ng, cn s ng gp tr tu nhiu t ngnh GD&amp;T, cc ngnh cc cp,  kin nhn dn. Trn c s ny, B s iu chnh ni dung i mi cho ph hp vi tnh hnh. Nm hc ny l nm hc u tin ca k hoch 5 nm nn c  ngha rt quan trng, cn phi c s quyt tm cao ca ton ngnh.</p>\r\n<table style="width: 550px;" class="image center" align="center" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img alt="B trng Phm V lun trao bng khen cho cc lnh o hon thnh xut sc nhim v nm hc" src="http://www.gdtd.vn/dataimages/201107/original/images549560_3.JPG" height="413" width="550" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="image_desc" align="center">B trng Phm V Lun trao bng khen cho cc n v hon thnh xut sc nhim v nm hc</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Cng ti hi ngh, B trng lu  cc S GD&amp;T mt s vn  mi. V&nbsp; thng t hng dn Ngh nh 115/2010/N-CP ngy 24/12/2010, B ang son tho, trong , c nhim v ca S GD&amp;T qun l mt s trng C, H  a phng, B trng  ngh&nbsp; cc S GD&amp;T nn tham mu vi UBND tnh  c th ch ng trong cc k hoch.V chng trnh CNTT trong i mi qun l, B ang c phn mm qun l v s trin khai rng trong tng lai, cc a phng c pht hin li g th phn nh v B, B s c hng dn v tho g. Ring vn  h tr SGK cho hc sinh ngho, va qua c thc t l c tnh h tr bng tin, nn b m hc sinh s dng vo vic khc. B trng&nbsp;  ngh cc gim c S quan tm iu chnh   khng  hc sinh no ngho phi b hc nh li Th tng Chnh ph  ch o.<br /> <strong> </strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong><em>NH GI T C S:</em></strong></p>\r\n<table style="width: 200px;" class="image rightside" align="right" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img alt="ng ng Vn Hng, gim c S GD Bc Ninh" src="http://www.gdtd.vn/dataimages/201107/original/images549562_3.JPG" height="153" width="200" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="image_desc" align="center">ng ng Vn Hng, Gim c S GD&amp;T Bc Ninh</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>*ng ng Vn Hng, Gim c S GD&amp;T tnh Bc Ninh:</strong><br /> <strong>Cn tip tc duy tr, pht trin cc cuc vn ng v phong tro. </strong><br /> Hiu qu m cc cuc vn ng, phong tro mang li l rt r rng. V th, chng ta nn duy tr cc cuc vn ng v nhng phong tro thi ua nh hin nay, nhm thc y  thc t gic, tinh thn say m t hc, t sng to trong phng php ging dy ca gio vin v  thc hc tp ca hc sinh. Bi cc cuc vn ng, phong tro thi ua trn c cc cp, cc ngnh v nhn dn ng h rt cao.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Cuc vn ng Hai khng tht s mang li nhiu hiu qu tch cc cho ngnh gio dc. Sau 4 nm trin khai, cuc vn ng khng ch cho x hi thy trch nhim ca ton ngnh trong vic hng n gio dc thc cht, m cn ch ra cho x hi thy nhng im tch cc m ngnh gio dc ang c. Ngnh v cc a phng  c s ng thun, tinh thn dm thng thn nhn vo nhng hn ch, dm chp nhn cht lng gio dc thc cht (d t l i khi thp)  t  sa cha v tin b, gip cho x hi tin tng hn.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Tuy nhin, bn cnh nhng a phng thc hin tt, th cng cn khng t ni trong qu trnh thc hin vn cn mt s vn  t nhiu gp phi vng mc v hn ch. Mi cng vic u cn phi c qu trnh v s ng thun ng h ca mi cp chnh quyn. Trong , vai tr ca ngnh GD&amp;T trong nh hng, h tr, tho g l rt quan trng.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table style="width: 200px;" class="image leftside" align="left" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img alt="ng Nguyn Khc Ho, gim c S H Tnh" src="http://www.gdtd.vn/dataimages/201107/original/images549563_2.JPG" height="160" width="200" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="image_desc" align="center">ng Nguyn Khc Ho,Gim c S GD&amp;T H Tnh</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">*<strong>ng Nguyn Khc Ho, Gim c S GD&amp;T H Tnh: X&nbsp; hi cn c ci nhn khch quan v&nbsp; gio dc </strong><br /> Trin khai Ch th 33/2006/CT-TTg ca Chnh ph, cht lng gio dc  c ci thin qua tng nm. Sau 4 nm, tc ng ca Hai khng l rt r rng. Thi  coi thi, chm thi ca cn b, gio vin  nn np, nghim tc hn trc rt nhiu. Hin tng tiu cc trong thi c nh lm bi cho hc sinh, g bi cho hc sinh, cho hc sinh s dng ti liu c ngn chn ht sc l kp thi.<br /> H Tnh chng ti khi thc hin cuc vn ng Hai khng  tng x l hng trm gio vin vi phm quy ch thi. C sau mi nm mnh tay nhng vi phm nh vy c ko gim i r rt. Thi c l mt p lc, nhng nu chng ta bit x l mt cch hi ha, bit lm cng tc tuyn truyn, gio dc, nng cao nhn thc mt cch hiu qu th kt qu mang li s thc cht.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">C&nbsp; nhn ti thy Hai khng l rt cn thit. X hi cn c ci nhn khch quan v gio dc, ng thy t l  hi cao mt cht l t du hi nghi vn, ti thy  l vic ht sc bnh thng sau nhng g chng ta dm chp nhn i mt  sa i v i mi&nbsp; cng tc thi c, dy v hc. Cuc vn ng Hai khng rt c  ngha, ht sc cn thit v phi tip tc c thc hin. V nu khng c cuc vn ng Hai khng tnh th n  khc.</p>\r\n<table style="width: 200px;" class="image leftside" align="left" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img alt="ng Phan Hng, gim c S GD tnh k Lk" src="http://www.gdtd.vn/dataimages/201107/original/images549564_1.jpg" height="136" width="200" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="image_desc" align="center">ng Phan Hng, Gim c S GD&amp;T k Lk</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">*<strong>ng Phan Hng, gim c S GD&amp;T tnh k Lk</strong>: <strong>Hiu qu cho pht trin gio dc </strong><br /> Cuc vn ng Hai khng  mang li nhng chuyn bin ht sc r nt. D t l nm hc ny mt s tnh c s gia tng t bin nhng ti khng ngh  l kt qu c vn  m ti tin t l y v c bn l s tng trng mang tnh quy lut v s n lc ca ngnh, ca i ng thy c gio, ca hc sinh cng nh ca ton x hi. Trong gio dc vic pht trin tt nhin s vn cn nhng hn ch ny, tn ti kia cn phi khc phc. Nhng nhn vo ton cc ca ngnh gio dc th s chuyn bin y l iu ng mng.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Phong tro thi ua Xy dng trng hc thn thin, hc sinh tch cc l mt phong tro mang tnh ton din. Bi phong tro   cp n rt nhiu vn : nng cao cht lng gio dc, i mi phng php dy v hc, ri xy dng k nng sng cho hc sinh, gio dc truyn thng, o cChnh v th, lm tt phong tro thi ua ny, ngnh gio dc s c iu kin  pht trin mt cch bn vng. Sau 4 nm thc hin cuc vn ng Hai khng cng vi s chuyn bin chung ca c nc, th nhng chuyn bin trong ngnh gio dc tnh k Lk l ht sc r nt.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table style="width: 200px;" class="image rightside" align="right" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img alt="G  S GD&amp;T TR VINH" src="http://www.gdtd.vn/dataimages/201107/original/images549565_5.JPG" height="156" width="200" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="image_desc" align="center">ng Triu Vn Phn, Gim c S GD&amp;T Tr Vinh</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>*ng Triu Vn Phn, Gim c S GD&amp;T Tr Vinh:</strong> <strong>C x hi chm lo cho gio dc </strong><br /> iu ti tm c nht l cc cuc vn ng v phong tro ca ngnh  to ra  thc c x hi cng chm lo cho gio dc. Tr Vinh l tnh c 30% ng bo dn tc Khmer, i sng cn kh khn, do  vic hc sinh b hc ba nm trc l mt vn  nan gii. Qua phong tro, cc ngnh cc cp, c x hi cng chm lo cho hc sinh ngho. T  t l hc sinh b hc ko gim xung 1%. Ba nm qua vic kin c ha trng hc c quan tm cha tng c. Vic gii ngn vn tri phiu Chnh ph lun vt ch tiu, nm 2010 gii ngn ti 200%. Tc l ng vn mt nm  xy dng trc. C th ni phong tro Xy dng trng hc thn thin, hc sinh tch cc  to bc t ph v cht lng gio dc  Tr Vinh.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>*ng V Vn Thng, Gim c S GD&amp;T ng Thp:</strong> <strong>Khi dy s sng to t c s </strong><br /> Phong tro Trng hc thn thin, hc sinh tch cc  to ra lung sinh kh mi cho gio dc. Hc sinh thm yu ngi trng mnh, qu hng mnh, t tin vo chnh mnh  phn u tr thnh ngi hu ch. Vn  gio dc k nng sng c quan tm. n ng Thp&nbsp; c rt nhiu m hnh  c sng to t s s nh: t nhn dn khuyn hc, xut pht t huyn Cao Lnh  c nhn ra c tnh; M hnh&nbsp; hc sinh THCS Nguyn Th Lu&nbsp; lm hng dn vin di tch M c Nguyn Sinh Sc; Hay mt b m ngho ch c 1 cng t m nui 5 con hc xong i hc  th trn M Th. Ngay nh k thi tt nghip THPT va qua, mt hc sinh ngho i chn tru  huyn Thp Mi   th khoa k thi. Xy dng Trng hc thn thin, hc sinh tch cc  gip&nbsp; x hi quan tm n gio dc hn, hc sinh rn luyn k nng sng tt hn.</p>\r\n<table style="width: 200px;" class="image leftside" align="left" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><a href="http://gdtd.vn/dataimages/201107/original/images549597_4.JPG"><img alt="ng L Hng Sn- Gim c S GD&amp;T thnh ph H Ch Minh" src="http://www.gdtd.vn/dataimages/201107/original/images549597_4.JPG" height="169" width="200" /></a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="image_desc" align="center">ng L Hng Sn, Gim c S GD&amp;T thnh ph H Ch Minh</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>*ng L Hng Sn- Gim c S GD&amp;T thnh ph H Ch Minh:</strong><br /> &nbsp;Hiu qu t c ln nht l to iu kin thun li cho hc sinh pht huy t duy, kh nng sng to, t hc ca mnh. Thy c gio&nbsp; dy hc chm cht theo tng c th, khng dy theo s ng hay theo t chng nh trc. Vic gio dc o c nhn cch, li sng, truyn thng cho cc em hc sinh c nhn rng. Thng qua cc tit hc, bi hc, kha hc lch s trong nh trng, chng ti quan tm b sung vo gio dc truyn thng lch s  a phng cng nh b tr t cc hot ng ngoi kha, dy k nng sng, nu nhng tm gng in hnh gip cc em rn luyn o c nhn cch v li sng tt p</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><br /> <strong>(GD&amp;T)</strong></p>\r\n</div>', '', 1, 3, 0, 21, '2011-12-13 08:07:00', 62, '', '2011-12-22 18:02:15', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-12-18 15:06:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 4, 0, 1, '', '', 0, 36, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(71, 'Thi tt nghip THPT 2012: Khng bt buc thi cm trng, xa chm cho', 'thi-tt-nghip-thpt-2012-khong-bt-buc-thi-cm-trng-xoa-chm-cheo', '', '<div class="fon33 mt1" style="text-align: justify;"><img alt="" src="data/giaoduc/demo/slide/photo04.jpg" height="433" width="577" /></div>\r\n<div class="fon33 mt1" style="text-align: justify;">K thi tt nghip THPT s khng cn bt buc t chc thi cm trng v chm cho gia cc tnh m thay vo  giao quyn ch ng cho gim c cc S GD-T. Bn cnh  b thanh tra y quyn ca B, a phng t thnh lp cc on thanh tra.</div>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"> l im quan trng trong d tho Thng t v vic sa i, b sung mt s iu ca quy ch thi tt nghip THPT m B GD-T ang ng ti xin  kin.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Cng theo d tho ny,  m bo cng tc coi thi cc a phng c th la chn cn b, ging vin tham gia thanh tra k thi trn a bn theo  ngh ca Ban ch o thi cp tnh.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Ngoi vic b thi cm, chm cho thng t d tho d kin m rng thnh phn tham gia lm th k v y vin Hi ng in sao  thi. C th: Th k v y vin Hi ng in sao  thi l chuyn vin ca S GD-T, cn b, gio vin, nhn vin ca cc trng ph thng. S lng th k v y vin do Gim c GD-T quy nh.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Gim c S GD-T ra quyt nh thnh lp Hi ng chm thi tt nghip ph thng trong , mi mn t lun c 2 t chm thi, m bo gio vin khng chm bi thi t lun ca hc sinh trng ph thng mnh ging dy.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Do thay i v phng thc t chc thi nn B GD-T cng  iu chnh nhng quy nh v phc kho bi thi. Theo , Hi ng phc kho c mt b phn lm phch bi thi t lun, c lp vi cc t chm thi. Hi ng phc kho c mt t chm trn my bi thi ca cc mn thi theo phng php trc nghim v b phn gim st trc tip, lin tc, thc hin nhim v theo hng dn chm thi trc nghim ca GD-T.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">B GD-T cho bit, sau khi tip nhn  kin ng gp cc im sa i ny li tip tc c bn lun ti Hi ngh thi v tuyn sinh nm 2012. Sau khi thng nht cc  kin, trong thng 2/2012, Thng t sa i quy ch thi tt nghip THPT s chnh thc c ban hnh.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><strong>(Dn tr)</strong></p>', '', 1, 3, 0, 22, '2011-12-13 08:12:24', 62, '', '2012-04-06 06:44:50', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-12-13 08:11:48', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 9, 0, 3, '', '', 0, 42, 'robots=\nauthor=');
