(76, 'PHNG PHP VIT SNG KIN KINH NGHIM', 'phng-phap-vit-sang-kin-kinh-nghim', '', '<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: #008080;"><strong><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">MT S VN  C BN V:</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"> PHNG PHP VIT SNG KIN KINH NGHIM</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><strong><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">1. Sng kin kinh nghim l g?</span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - Sng kin l  kin sinh ra t nhng nhn xt mi</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - Kinh nghim l nhng hiu bit do trng thy, nghe thy, do tng tri m c.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small; font-family: Times New Roman;">Kinh nghim l nhng tri th do qui np v thc nghim em li,  c chnh l v phn lai  lp thnh c s ca khoa hc. Nh vy ni ti kinh nghim l ni n <strong>nhng vic  lm, c kt qu,  c kim nghim trong thc t </strong>, khng phi l nhng vic&nbsp; d nh hay cn trong  ngh.</span></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong><em> sng kin kinh nghim </em></strong> <em>l nhng tri thc, k nng, k xo m ngi vit tch ly&nbsp; c trong thc tin cng tc ging dy v gio dc, bng nhng hat ng c th  khc phc c nhng kh khn m vi nhng bin php thng thng khng th gii quyt c , gp phn nng cao hiu qu r rt&nbsp; trong cng tc ca ngi gio vin.<img style="float: left;" src="data/giaoduc/photo/20799745_images1612093_Ky-ket.jpg" alt="" height="230" width="307" /></em></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><strong><span style="font-size: small; font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><strong><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">2. Nhng yu cu c bn i vi mt sng kin kinh nghim</span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Khi vit mt sng kin kinh nghim, tc gi cn lm r <strong>tnh mc ch, tnh thc tin, tnh sng to khoa hc v kh nng vn dng, m rng SKKN </strong> nh th no?Sau y l biu hin c th cn t c ca nhng yu cu trn:</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>+ Tnh mc ch: &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -  ti  gii quyt c nhng mu thun, nhng kh khn g c tnh cht thi s trong cng tc ging dy, gio dc hc sinh, trong cng tc ph trch i TNTP.H Ch Minh?</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; - Tc gi vit SKKN nhm mc ch g? ( nng cao nghip v cng tc ca bn thn,  trao i kinh nghim vi ng nghip,  tham gia nghin cu khoa hc )</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>+ Tnh thc tin :</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; - Tc gi trnh by c nhng s kin  din ra trong thc tin cng tc ging dy, gio dc ca mnh, cng tc i TNTP  ni mnh cng tc.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; - Nhng kt lun c rt ra trong  ti&nbsp; phi l s khi qut ha t nhng s thc phong ph, nhng hat ng c th  tin hnh ( cn trnh vic sao chp sch v mang tnh l thuyt n thun, thiu tnh thc tin )</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>+ Tnh sng to khoa hc:</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; - Trnh by c c s l lun, c s thc tin lm ch da cho vic gii quyt vn   nu ra trong  ti.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; - Trnh by mt cch r rng,mch lc cc bc tin hnh trong SKKN</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; - Cc phng php tin hnh mi m, c o.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; - Dn chng cc t liu, s liu v kt qu chnh xc lm ni bt&nbsp; tc dng , hiu qu ca SKKN  p dng.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Tnh khoa hc ca mt  ti SKKN c th hin c trong ni dung ln hnh thc trnh by  ti cho nn khi vit SKKN, tc gi cn ch  c 2 im ny.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>+ Kh nng vn dng v m rng SKKN:</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; - Trnh by, lm r hiu qu khi p dng SKKN ( c dn chng cc kt qu,cc s liu  so snh hiu qu ca cch lm mi so vi &nbsp;cch lm c )</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; - Ch ra c nhng iu kin cn bn, nhng bi hc kinh nghim  p dng c hiu qu SKKN, ng thi phn tch cho thy trin vng trong vic vn dng v pht trin SKKN  trnh by (  ti c th vn dng trong phm vi no? C th m rng, pht trin  ti nh th no? )</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  m bo c nhng yu cu trn, i hi ngi vit SKKN :</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <em>+ Phi c thc t (  gp nhng mu thun, kh khn c th trong thc tin cng tc ging dy, gio dc hc sinh, trong vic gii quyt nhng vn  thc tin ca cng tc i TNTP  a phng, c s ni mnh cng tc )</em></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><em><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; + Phi c l lun lm c s cho vic tm ti bin php gii quyt vn .</span></span></em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><em><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; + C phng php, bit trnh by SKKN khoa hc, r rng, mch lc:</span></span></em></p>\r\n<p style="text-indent: 36pt; text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><em><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp; - Nm vng cu trc ca mt  ti, bit cn nhc, chn lc t tn cc  mc ph hp ni dung,th hin tnh logic ca  ti</span></span></em></p>\r\n<p style="text-indent: 36pt; text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><em><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp; -Nm vng cc phng php nghin cu khoa hc.Khi xc nh mt phng php no  c s dng trong vic nghin cu  ti, tc gi cn phi xc nh c cc yu t c bn: Mc tiu ca vic thc hin phng php?Phng php c p dng vi i tng no?Ni dung thng tin cn thu c qua phng php ?Nhng bin php c th  tin hnh phng php nghin cu c hiu qu?</span></span></em></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"><em>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; + Thu thp y  cc t liu, s liu lin quan n kinh nghim trnh by. Cc s liu c chn lc v trnh by trong nhng bng thng k thch hp, c tc dng lm ni bt vn  m tc gi mun chng minh, dn chng.</em> </span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><strong><span style="font-size: small; font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><strong><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">3. Mc  v cch gii thiu SKKN:</span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; C th&nbsp; chia SKKN thnh 2 mc  nh sau:</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; + <strong>Tng thut kinh nghim</strong>: tc gi k li nhng suy ngh, nhng vic  lm,nhng cch lm  mang li nhng kt qu nh th no?  mc  tng thut, tc gi cn:</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;- Lm ni bt cc bin php c tnh cht sng to, c tc dng tt  gip tc gi khc phc kh khn, mang li kt qu trong cng tc ging dy, gio dc  c s ( m t cng vic tin hnh theo trnh t logic).</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - M t cc kt qu  t c t vic p dng cc bin php  tin hnh.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - Ch ra nhng bi hc kinh nghim cn thit.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Tuy nhin <span style="text-decoration: underline;">cn trnh vic k l di dng, dn tri bin bn SKKN thnh mt bn bo co thnh tch hoc mt bn bo co tng kt n thun. iu ny s lm cho bn SKKN km gi tr, thiu tnh thuyt phc.</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; + <strong>Phn tch kinh nghim:</strong>  mc  ny, tc gi cn thc hin c cc yu cu nh  mc  tng thut kinh nghim. Ngai ra cn nhn xt, nh gi nhng u im, tc ng v nhng mt cn hn ch ca SKKN&nbsp;  thc hin,hng pht trin nng cao ca  ti ( nu c th ). Trong vic phn tch&nbsp; , tc gi cn phi :</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; - M t cc bin php  tin hnh trong  ti v gii thch  ngha,l do la chn nhng bin php v tc dng ca chng.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; - Nu c mi quan h gia cc bin php vi c im i tng, vi nhng iu kin iu kin khch quan.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; - Rt ra nhng kt lun khi qut&nbsp; hng dn cho vic p dng c hiu qu SKKN ( nhng iu kin cn bo m, nhng bi hc kinh nghim ) v m rng, pht trin SKKN.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><strong><span style="font-size: small; font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><strong><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">4.Cc bc tin hnh vit mt SKKN: </span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-indent: 36pt; text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small; font-family: Times New Roman;">+<strong>Chn  ti</strong>&nbsp; ( t tn  ti ):</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-indent: 36pt; text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp; Cc vn  c th chn  vit SKKN rt phong ph, a dng, bao gm nhiu lnh vc nh :</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-indent: 36pt; text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp; - Kinh nghim trong vic ging dy ( mt chng, mt bi, mt&nbsp; ni dung kin thc c th )</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-indent: 36pt; text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp; - Kinh nghim trong vic gio dc hc sinh</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; - Kinh nghim trong vic bi dng, ph o hc sinh</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; - Kinh nghim trong vic t chc mt hat ng gio dc c th cho hc sinh ( V d: hat ng gio dc ngai gi ln lp, cng tc x hi  )</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; - Kinh nghim gii quyt nhng vn  kh khn, phc tp trong khi tin hnh cc hat ng, cc phong tro ca i TNTP. H Ch Minh ( VD: T chc sinh hot sao nhi ng, bi dng ph trch sao,bi dng nng lc t qun cho i vin, bi dng BCH i, bi dng ph trch chi i,trin khai chng trnh rn luyn i vin,xy dng mt m hnh hat ng i, t chc bi dng mt s k nng c th cho ph trch chi i, BCH i,ph trch sao)</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; Khi tin hnh cng vic vit SKKN, cng vic u tin ca tc gi l cn suy ngh&nbsp; la chn mt tn  ti ph hp. Trong nghin cu khoa hc ( vit SKKN ) vic xc nh tn  ti c  ngha quan trng s mt, i khi n cn quan trng hn c vic gii quyt  ti. Vic xc nh tn  ti chnh xc&nbsp; c tc dng nh hng gii quyt vn  cho tc gi,gip cho tc gi bit tp trung s nghin cu vo vn  cn gii quyt, trnh c s lan man, lc .</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; Tn  ti chnh l mt mu thun, mt vn  trong thc tin ging dy, gio dc m tc gi cn ang phn vn, trn tr, tm cch gii quyt, lm sng t. Tn  ti mang tnh ch th, i hi ngi vit phi c s hng th vi n, phi kin tr v quyt tm vi n. V mt ngn t tn  ti phi t cc yu cu :</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; - ng ng php.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; -   , r ngha, khng lm cho ngi c c th hiu theo  khc.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; - Xc nh c phm vi, ni dung nghin cu c th ca  ti, cn trnh vn  qu chung chung hoc c phm vi qu rng kh c th gii quyt trn vn trong mt  ti. </span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-indent: 36pt; text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><strong><span style="font-size: small; font-family: Times New Roman;">+ Vit  cng chi tit:</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; y l mt cng vic rt cn thit trong vic vit SKKN. Nu b qua vic ny, tc gi s khng nh hng c mnh cn phi vit ci g, cn thu thp nhng t liu g v l thuyt v thc tin ,cn trnh by nhng s liu ra sao? Vic chun b  cng cng chi tit bao nhiu th cng vic vit SKKN cng thun li by nhiu. Khi xy dng  cng chi tit, tc gi cn:</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; - Xy dng c mt dn bi chi tit vi cc  mc r rng, hp logic, ch ra c nhng  cn vit trong tng  mc c th.Vic ny cn c cn nhc k lng sao cho  phn nh ni dung  ti, khng tha v cng khng thiu.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; - Thit k cc bng thng k s liu ph hp, cc mu phiu iu tra kho st, hnh nh phc v thit thc cho vic minh ha, dn chng cho  ti.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-indent: 36pt; text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp; -Kin quyt lai b nhng  mc,nhng bng thng k, nhng thng tin khng cn thit cho  ti.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>+ Tin hnh thc hin  ti:</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; -Tc gi tm c cc ti liu lin quan n  ti, ghi nhn nhng cng vic  thc hin trong thc tin ( bin php, cc bc tin hnh, kt qu c th ), thu thp cc s liu  dn chng.Tc gi nn lu tr cc t liu thu thp c theo tng lai. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Nn s dng cc ti h s ring cho tng vn  thun tin cho vic tm kim, tng hp thng tin.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; - Trong qu trnh thu thp ti liu cn tip tc &nbsp;xem xt chnh sa  cng chi tit cho ph hp vi tnh hnh thc t.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>+ Vit bn tho SKKN</strong> theo  cng  chun b.Khi vit SKKN tc gi cn ch  y l lai vn bn bo co khoa hc cho nn ngn ng vit cn ngn gn, xc tch, chnh xc. Cn trnh s dng ngn ng ni hoc k l di dng nhng khng din t c thng tin cn thit.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>+ Han chnh bn SKKN</strong>, nh my, in n.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><strong><span style="font-size: small; font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><strong><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">5. Kt cu ca mt sng kin kinh nghim</span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><strong><span style="font-size: small; font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<table style="border-collapse: collapse;" border="1" cellpadding="0