e="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>+ t vn : (</strong>hoc<strong> L do chn  ti )</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; Phn ny tc gi ch yu trnh by l do chn  ti. C th tc gi cn trnh by c cc  chnh sau y:</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; * Nu r hin tng ( vn  ) trong thc tin ging dy, gio dc, cng tc i m tc gi  chn  vit SKKN.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; *  ngha v tc dng ( v mt l lun ) ca hin tng ( vn  )  trong cng tc ging dy, gio dc, cng tc i.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; * Nhng mu thun gia thc trng ( c nhng bt hp l, c nhng iu cn ci tin sa i ) vi yu cu mi i hi phi c gii quyt.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; T nhng  , tc gi khng nh l do mnh chn vn   vit SKKN.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>+ Gii quyt vn : ( </strong>hoc <strong>Ni dung sng kin kinh nghim )</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; y l phn quan trng, ct li nht ca mt SKKN, theo chng ti tc gi nn trnh by theo 4 mc chnh sau y:</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong><em>* C s l lun ca vn :</em></strong> Trong mc ny tc gi cn trnh by tm tt nhng l lun, l thuyt  c tng kt ,bao gm nhng khi nim, nhng kin thc c bn v vn  c chn  vit SKKN.  chnh l nhng c s l lun c tc dng <strong>nh hng cho vic&nbsp; nghin cu, tm kim nhng gii php, bin php</strong> nhm khc phc nhng mu thun, kh khn tc gi  trnh by trong phn t vn .</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; <strong><em>* Thc trng ca vn :</em></strong>Tc gi trnh by nhng thun li, kh khn m tc gi  gp phi trong vn  m tc gi  chn  vit SKKN. iu quan trng trong phn ny l m t,lm ni bt &nbsp;nhng kh khn ,nhng mu thun m tc gi ang tm cch gii quyt, ci tin.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; <strong><em>* Cc bin php  tin hnh  gii quyt vn  :</em></strong> Trnh by trnh t nhng bin php, cc bc c th&nbsp;  tin hnh  gii quyt vn , trong  c nhn xt v vai tr, tc dng, hiu qu&nbsp; ca tng bin php hoc tng bc .</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong><em>* Hiu qu ca SKKN:</em></strong> Trong mc ny cn trnh by c cc  :</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -  p dng SKKN  lp no,khi no, cho i tng c th no ?</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - Trnh by r kt qu c th khi p dng SKKN ( c i chiu so snh vi kt qu khi tin hnh cng vic theo cch c )</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Vic t tiu  cho cc  chnh trn y cn c cn nhc, chn lc sao cho ph hp vi  ti  chn v din t c ni dung ch yu m tc gi mun trnh by trong  ti.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>+ Kt lun :</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; Cn trnh by c :</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -  ngha ca SKKN i vi cng vic ging dy, gio dc , trong vic yin hnh cc hat ng i hoc thc hin cc nhim v ca ngi gio vin, ngi ph trch i.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - Nhng nhn nh chung ca tc gi v vic p dng &nbsp;v kh nng pht trin ca SKKN.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - Nhng bi hc kinh nghim c rt ra t qu trnh p dng SKKN ca bn thn</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - Nhng  kin  xut ( vi B GD-T, S GD-T, Phng GD-T, Lnh o trng ty theo tng  ti )&nbsp;  p dng SKKN c hiu qu.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small; font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Tm li, cng vic vit SKKN thc s l nt cng vic khoa hc, nghim tc i hi ngi vit phi kin nhn, phi c s u t tr tu , cng sc v thi gian.  han tan khng phi l mt vic d dng. Hy vng rng vi mt s gi  trn y c th gip cc bn ng nghip mt s  tng chnh trong cng vic vit SKKN, gp phn nng cao cht lng ging dy v gio dc ca cc bn  a phng.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-indent: 36pt; text-align: justify; margin: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: small; color: #008080;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"><strong>Chc cc bn thnh cng.!</strong> </span></span></p>', '', 1, 3, 0, 20, '2011-12-18 06:06:43', 62, '', '2011-12-22 18:58:56', 62, 0, '0000-