(74, 'Mi hc sinh u gi ti l m', 'mi-hc-sinh-u-gi-toi-la-m', '', '<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"> Sut 31 nm cng tc trong ngnh gio dc, ti lun nhn c s tin yu ca ngi dn. H cng ti ti bn m trng dng lp, h cng ti bc cu qua sui cho con em i hc Mi khi ti ti lp, mi hc sinh u gi ti bng m.<br /></span><img style="float: right;" src="data/giaoduc/demo/slide/photo05.jpg" alt="alt" height="202" width="269" /><br /></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: justify;">C gio Hong Th Hu, Hiu trng Trng Tiu hc Phong Chu, th x Ph Th, tnh Ph Th trn trng v xc ng khi k v tnh cm thn thng t nhng ph huynh v hc sinh  dnh cho mnh.</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: justify;">Lin tc l gio vin dy gii cp tnh t khi bt u ngh gio (nm 1981), l chin s thi ua cp c s v cp tnh sut nhng nm hc 2000 n 2009, trc tip ging dy v bi dng 11 hc sinh gii quc gia v trn 400 hc sinh gii cp th x v cp tnh..., c gio Hong Th Hu  ginh c nhiu danh hiu, bng khen ca tnh v cc B, ngnh Trung ng trao tng.</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: justify;">C Hu sinh ra v ln ln ti mt x ngho huyn min ni Cm Kh vi c m tr thnh c gio ca lng qu ngho y. Khi c m tr thnh hin thc, c lun ghi nh li Bc dy: V li ch trm nm th phi trng ngi. Coi ngh gio khng ch l ngh dy hc n thun, c Hu xc nh gio dc tiu hc, c bit l i vi hc sinh lp 1 c  ngha nh t vin gch cho nn mng cho s nghip sau ny ca mi hc sinh. Nu cc em hc sinh lp 1  chn hc, liu khi cc em bc vo mi trng THCS, THPT s th no?</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: justify;">Thi gian ging dy  Thanh Sn, Cm Kh c khng ch vn ng hc sinh vng cao, hc sinh c hon cnh kh khn ra lp m  vn dng linh hot cc phng php ging dy tch cc ph hp vi tnh hnh thc t  a phng. C  chu kh my m lm  dng dy hc,  chi cho tr t nhng nguyn liu r tin  h tr cho vic ging dy t kt qu tt.</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: justify;">C thc hin tt cng tc x hi ho gio dc thng qua cc hnh thc to sn chi cho tr nh: Thi k chuyn lch s, thi tm hiu v qu hng t nc, d hi vn hc, ton hc, thi thn ng t Vit... to cho tr nim hng th tht s tch cc gip  nhau cng vn ln hc tp. V vy, cht lng gio dc ca lp c ch nhim hng nm thng dn u nh trng v ng u huyn.</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: justify;">Nm 2002, khi c phn cng lm Hiu trng Trng tiu hc Phong Chu, c Hu  <b>l</b>nh o trng t mt n v ng tp cui ca th x Ph Th (nm hc 2001-2002) tr thnh tp th lao ng tin tin, tp th lao ng xut sc, n v l c u bc tiu hc nm 2008, c Tng Lin on Lao ng Vit Nam tng danh hiu C quan vn ho xut sc.</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: justify;">Nh li thi im khi mi v trng, c Hu bi ngi:  l ngi trng nm gia th x nhng kh khn v mi mt. C s vt cht thiu thn, trng c 16 lp hc nhng ch c 12 phng hc, mt s lp phi hc hai ca, phng chc nng cha y  phi ghp vi lp hc, cng trnh ph ca hc sinh lm theo kiu c khng m bo v sinh, trnh  i ng gio vin khng p ng vi vic i mi chng trnh gio dc...</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: justify;">Vi nhng n lc khng bit mt mi, c  tng bc lm xoay chuyn nh trng theo hng tch cc nh m hi ngh thm d  kin ca tp th gio vin, ph huynh trong ton trng, thng qua  thy c nhng im mnh ca mi c nhn  nhn ln thnh sc mnh tp th. ng thi lm tt cng tc tham mu vi cp u, chnh quyn a phng, thc hin x hi ho gio dc  tng bc xy dng thm cc nh lp hc, cc phng chc nng theo tiu ch trng chun quc gia mc  1.</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: justify;"> khc phc cht lng gio vin cn hn ch, c Hu  thnh lp i gio vin ct cn do chnh c lm t trng  cng nhau trao i kinh nghim, gip  nhau trong chuyn mn v t chc i hc tp kinh nghim  cc n v bn; t chc cc lp tp hun v i mi phng php dy hc. Kt qu, s lng gio vin dy gii ca trng hin ng tp u th x, nhiu gio vin dy gii cp tnh v 1 gio vin dy gii cp quc gia. Khng ch c vy, c Hu l gio vin lun i u trong cng tc nghin cu khoa hc. Nm hc 2007-2008, c  c 2 sng kin kinh nghim d thi ton quc t gii xut sc v c Ban iu hnh D n Gio dc tr kh khn (PEDC) trao gii thng cho tr thit thi ca trng l 278 triu ng. y l ngun kinh ph gip  trc tip cho 64 hc sinh khuyt tt, hc sinh c hon cnh kh khn ca trng.</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: justify;">ng ng Vn Hng, Trng phng Gio dc th x Ph Th nhn xt: C Hu  dnh ton b tnh yu, tm sc v ti nng ca mnh vo s nghip gio dc a phng  mang n cho tr mt nguyn l gio dc tng d m khng h d: Mi ngy n trng l mt ngy vui. V thc t chng minh c hon thnh xut sc nhim v d  bt c cng v no hay ngi trng no.</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: justify;">Vi nhng thnh tch  t c trong cng tc ging dy v lnh o, c gio Hong Th Hu  c Hi ng thi ua khen thng tnh Ph Th  ngh xt tng danh hiu cao qu Nh gio u t nm 2010.</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: right;" align="right"><strong>TTXVN</strong></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p></p>', '', 1, 3, 0, 24, '2011-12-18 05:24:57', 62, '', '2011-12-23 06:46:07', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-12-18 05:20:09', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 10, 0, 2, '', '', 0, 25, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(81, 'Nn sm trang b phng php lun trit hc cho HS', 'nen-sm-trang-b-phng-phap-lun-trit-hc-cho-hs', '', '<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">(GD&amp;T)-Sinh vin s mn Trit hc dng nh  tr thnh chuyn xa nh tri t. Nhiu ging vin ging dy mn hc ny cng t vn  cp thit cn i mi cch dy v hc Trit hc. Nhng,  ngi hc thc s hiu c s cn thit ca mn hc ny, kh hn na l thc s yu thch mn hc vn l bi ton v cng nan gii.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong><img src="http://www.gdtd.vn/dataimages/201111/original/images595317_1.jpg" alt="Hc sinh ang lm bi" title="AAAAAAAAAAAAAA" style="float: right;" border="0" height="145" width="195" /></strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><strong>Sinh vin s Trit</strong><br /> <span style="font-size: 8pt;">Trong ging ng i hc, mn Trit hc dng nh l mi kinh hong i vi rt nhiu sinh vin, k c nhng sinh vin kh, gii. Khng t sinh vin th nhn mnh kh c th tnh to n cui gi khi hc Trit, cng khng t sinh vin ngm ngi  trt hc bng hoc thm ch l c nm hc v mn hc ny.<br /> <br /> <span style="font-size: 8pt;"> Tru tng, kh hiu l cm t thng gp nht khi cc bn sinh vin nhn xt v mn hc ny. Thy Linh  sinh vin Hc vin Bo ch v tuyn truyn tm s khi hc Trit: Thc s, d  rt c gng nhng hu nh em khng hiu c bao nhiu ni dung bi dy trn lp. D thy ging bi rt nhit tnh nhng do ton nhng thut ng chuyn ngnh, qu khi qut, tru tng nn bi hc khng th vo u ni. Sau , em  c gng c sch trc  nh nhng tnh hnh cng khng ci thin c bao nhiu.<br /> <br /> <span style="font-size: 8pt;"> Li ging dy cn mang tnh kinh vin, gio iu, bn thn mn hc vi nhng nguyn l, quy lut, phm tr kh hiu khin sinh vin s dn n chn  nh. Nhng, nhiu sinh vin cho rng y l mn hc t ng dng trong thc t khng gip ch g cho cng vic tng lai nn l l, cp tit, ngh hc Chnh v vy, t l sinh vin thi li mn Trit hc lun rt cao.<br /> <br /> <span style="font-size: 8pt;"> Ngay c nhng sinh vin theo ngnh Trit hc cng t nhn mnh vt v vi mn hc ny. Nhiu nguyn nhn gp li khin cho ngnh Trit hc ngy cng t c sinh vin la chn. im chun vo ngnh ny thng khng cao nhng cc trng vn phi tuyn n NV2, NV3 mi mong  ch tiu.<br /> <br /> <span style="font-size: 8pt;"> <strong>To mi trng trit hc t  lp 1</strong><br /> <br /> <span style="font-size: 8pt;"> GS.VS Nguyn Canh Toan cho rng, thc trng dy  hc Trit hc hin nay ging nh vic em hat ging tt gieo ln tha rung cha c chun bi. L mt mn hc kh nhng hoc sinh t ph thng vao ai hoc cha c chun bi mt cach y u, khoa hoc cho vic hoc trit hoc. Ngc lai, cac mn hoc khac it nhiu a co s chun bi t thp ln cao  bc ph thng.<br /> <br /> <span style="font-size: 8pt;"> Theo GS.VS Nguyn Canh Toan,  trng ph thng, cho n ht lp 11, cha nn co mn hoc trit hoc nhng nn dung 11 nm t lp 1 n lp 11  tao mi trng v phng phap lun cho hoc sinh. Sau 11 nm tich luy, ln lp 12 cho hoc sinh hoc mt giao trinh trit hoc duy vt bin chng gon, nhe, b ich va khi ln n ai hoc thi sinh vin a co kha nng i su, m rng, ln cao tuy theo nhu cu va hng thu cua tng ngi.<br /> <br /> <span style="font-size: 8pt;"> V vic to mi trng phng php lun cho hc sinh, GS.VS Nguyn Cnh Ton a ra 1 v d sinh ng t vic dy hc ton cho hc sinh lp 1: Lam phep cng 2+9 oi hoi s thng minh la thay 2+9 bng 9+2 (tinh giao hoan cua phep cng): tn dung c s ln la 9, chi cn m thm: 9 cng 1 la 10, 10 cng 1 la 11. Nu la phep cng 8+9 thi cach trn khng co li nhiu vi 8 cung ln nn phai nghi cach khac i 9 thanh 10 - 1 thi se co 8+10 thanh 18, 18 tr 1 thanh 17... Chi cn vi my phep tinh n gian nh trn a co th giao duc c t duy bin chng cho hoc tro, nu giao vin co thm tai nng s pham.<br /> <br /> <span style="font-size: 8pt;"> Nhn nh trong bi cnh hin nay, dy Trit th no  chinh phc c ngi hc l mt vn  kh khn, TS Nguyn Th Toan - Khoa Trit hc, Trng i hc S phm H Ni l gii nguyn nhn ch yu do mu thun gia yu cu ca b mn vi trnh  thc t ca i ng ging vin; gia khi lng kin thc  s vi thi gian dy hc b rt ngn; mu thun gia kin thc l lun v thc tin cuc sng; mu thun gia yu cu i mi phng php dy hc theo hng hin i vi iu kin vt cht, trang thit b thiu thn, lc hu v mu thun gia yu cu ca mn hc vi quan nim ca x hi v v tr, vai tr ca mn hc.<br /> <br /> <span style="font-size: 8pt;"> TS Nguyn Th Toan cho rng,  Trit hc thc s cn ch ng i vi ngi hc, cn khc phc c nhng im kh trn bng nhng gii php ng b, ton din: s ch o st sao ca cc cp cc ngnh; i mi ni dung chng trnh, gio trnh mt cch khoa hc; u t c s vt cht, trang thit b dy hc hp l; i mi ni dung, phng php, phng tin dy hc theo hng tin tin; thay i  thc, thi  v phng php hc tp; thay i nhn thc x hi v v tr, vai tr mn hc; to lp mi trng kinh t - chnh tr - vn ha lnh mnh thun li cho vic dy Trit hc... </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><strong>(GD&amp;T)</strong></span></p>', '', 1, 4, 0, 28, '2011-12-19 09:43:26', 62, '', '2012-04-06 13:10:17', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-12-19 09:42:10', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 10, 0, 2, '', '', 0, 54, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(91, 'Cn tip tc i mi cng tc thi ua, khen thng trong khi ng ', 'cn-tip-tc-i-mi-cong-tac-thi-ua-khen-thng-trong-khi-ng-', '', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>(TKT)- Ngy 29/11 ti H Ni, Ban T chc Trung ng phi hp vi Ban Thi ua Khen thng Trung ng t chc Hi&nbsp; tho i mi cng tc thi ua, khen thng Khi ng. Tham d v ch tr hi tho c cc ng ch: Nguyn Vn Quynh, y vin Trung ng ng, Ph trng ban Ban T chc Trung ng; Trn Th H, Th trng B Ni v, Trng ban Ban Thi ua  Khen thng Trung ng cng 10 n v ca khi ng  trung ng v 10 tnh y i din cho 63 tnh, thnh ph trong c nc.</p>\r\n<p align="justify">Hi tho nhm lm r v tr, vai tr, thc trng ca cng tc thi ua, khen thng t  kin ngh,  xut nhng ni dung i mi cng tc thi ua, khen thng trong khi ng, gp phn xy dng  n i mi cng tc thi ua, khen thng trnh B Chnh tr, tin ti  xut sa i Lut Thi ua, Khen thng, p ng nhng yu cu, nhim v xy dng v bo v T quc trong tnh hnh mi.</p>\r\n<p align="center"><img src="http://www.thiduakhenthuongvn.org.vn/TDKT/images/stories/KhoiDang1.JPG" alt="Active Image" height="319" width="477" /></p>\r\n<div align="justify"></div>\r\n<p align="justify">Ti hi tho, cc i biu  tp trung lm r mt s vn  v h thng cc quy nh ca ng i vi cng tc thi ua, khen thng; nhn thc quan im v nh gi cng tc lnh o, ch o ca cc cp y ng i vi vic qun trit, trin khai cc ch chng, chnh sch v thi ua, khen thng trong ng; nhng nt c th trong cng tc ch o, t chc cc phong tro thi ua, hnh thc, ni dung thi ua trong khi ng hin nay; cc danh hiu thi au, cc hnh thc khen thng v chnh sch khen thng i vi t chc cc c s ng v ng vin; cp c thm quyn ban hnh cc hnh thc khen thng, cng nhn cc danh hiu thi ua, tuyn trnh khen thng trong khi ng Hu ht cc  kin u thng nht cho rng, i mi v cng tc thi ua, khen thng trong khi ng l vic ht sc cn thit  gp phn tip tc pht huy hiu qu cc phong tro thi ua, lm cho phong tro thi ua thc s pht trin su rng trong khi ng, gp phn thc y pht trin kinh t - x hi chung ca t nc.</p>\r\n<p align="center"><img src="http://www.thiduakhenthuongvn.org.vn/TDKT/images/stories/KhoiDang2.JPG" alt="Active Image" height="332" width="494" /></p>\r\n<div align="justify"></div>\r\n<p align="justify">Cc i biu cng  ngh, cng vi vic nng cao cht lng cng tc thi ua, khen thng bng cch kp thi khen thng, tuyn dng cc c nhn, tp th c thnh tch xut sc&nbsp; th cn hon thin h thng vn bn quy phm php lut v thi ua, khen thng st vi thc tin. Cng tc kim tra, thanh tra vic thc hin php lut Nh nc v thi ua, khen thng nn c tng cng, thc hin n gin ha th tc hnh chnh trong lnh vc thi ua, khen thng. Tip tc tp trung nghin cu k  i mi sp xp t chc b my lm cng tc thi ua, khen thng cc cp theo hng tp trung thng nht t trung ng n a phng. Ngoi ra, cn ch trng bi dng nng cao chuyn mn, nghip v cho i ng p ng nhim v cng tc thi ua, khen thng trong thi k cng nghip ha  hin i ha t nc.</p>', '', 1, 3, 0, 36, '2011-12-22 18:38:37', 62, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-12-22 18:38:37', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 1, 0, 1, '', '', 0, 27, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(82, 'Khan him ngun nhn lc cht lng cao ti Vit Nam', 'khan-him-ngun-nhan-lc-cht-lng-cao-ti-vit-nam', '', '<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 10pt;">Ngy hi Nhn s Vit Nam 2011 do T chc T vn Gio dc Vit Nam (EduViet), Hi Doanh nhn tr Vit Nam, Din n nhn s v Cu lc b Gim c Nhn s Vit Nam t chc ngy 13/11 ti Thnh ph H Ch Minh tip tc ging ln hi chung cnh bo v s khan him ngun nhn lc cht lng cao trong cc doanh nghip.</span></p>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;" class="body_description"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;">Theo b Nguyn Th Hng, nguyn B trng B Lao ng Thng binh v X hi, Ch tch Ngy hi Nhn s Vit Nam 2011, s hi nhp quc t su rng buc cc doanh nghip Vit Nam phi thay i t duy v cch thc qun tr, trong  c cng tc qun tr nhn s l then cht.<span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;">\r\n<table style="width: 201px; float: right;" align="left" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="text-align: right;"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><img alt="nh minh ha" src="http://doanthanhnien.vn/Uploads/0nhaluc.jpg" height="151" hspace="5" vspace="5" width="201" /></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="middle" align="center"><span style="color: #0000ff; font-size: 10pt;">nh minh ha</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</span></span><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;"></span></div>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;">Ngun nhn lc cht lng cao s quyt nh n s pht trin kinh t x hi v  cng l mt trong 3 t ph m Vit Nam s phi thc hin trong thi gian ti. ng V Quc Thng, Ch tch Hi Doanh nhn tr Vit Nam, Ch tch Hi ng qun tr kim Tng gim c ng Tm Group cho hay, y l thi im cng tc nhn s gp kh khn nht. Nhng ch doanh nghip  ngm n khng ch vi li sut m cn vi cng tc nhn s, nht l ngun nhn lc cht lng cao. Kho st ca ph gio s, tin s L Qun, Trng ban t chc Ngy Nhn s Vit Nam 2011, Ch tch Hi ng qun tr EduViet cho thy, trn 30% doanh nghip gp kh khn trong tuyn dng nhn s, trong khi phi cn t 1-4 thng mi c th tuyn c ch tiu. Nu ch da vo nhn lc gi r v ngun ti nguyn thin nhin sn c, s pht trin ca doanh nghip s khng vng bn.</span></div>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;"> Vit Nam lao ng c cht lng khng cao, chi ph tuyn dng thp, thi gian o to nhanh, chi ph sa thi cng thp nn ct gim nhn s trong bi cnh khng hong kinh t ang l hot ng u tin ca khng t doanh nghip. Mt thc trng khng km phn nhc nhi cng c tham lun ca b Trn Th Tuyt,Ging vin i hc La Trobe kim ging vin trng i hc Ngoi ng, i hc Quc gia H Ni phn nh, trong khi ngun nhn lc cht lng cao l sinh vin mi tt nghip i hc ang trn trc tm khng ra vic lm th cc doanh nghip cng ku ca v kh khn trong tuyn dng nhn lc. Cung v cu ngun nhn lc cht lng cao  Vit Nam vn cha tm c hng i chung. Trch nhim ny khng ch thuc v nh trng v cc trng i hc cng hin ang qu ti, cn cc trng t li trong tnh trng km ci. Ngay c doanh nghip l ngi s dng nhn lc cng t ra lm khch i vi nh trng, rt t khi tham gia trc tip vo cc khu t chc, o to nhn lc. Thm ch c  kin cn cho rng, c ch xin cho vn cn len li trong cc doanh nghip v hnh thnh nn thi  xem thng nhn ti. </span></div>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;" class="body_description">\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;">Di gc  l ch doanh nghip, ng Vn c Mi, Tng gim c Tp on Vissan cho rng: D  qua o to ngh hay tt nghip i hc, cao ng, ngi lao ng Vit Nam vn phi c doanh nghip o to li. Doanh nghip cn nhn s cht lng  3 im cn bn: C nng lc nghin cu, sng to; k nng qun l; tay ngh, k hoch sn xut. V cc gii php tho g bi ton thiu nhn lc cht lng cao, ngoi vic nhn mnh cng tc o to ca nh trng v s tham gia ca doanh nghip, nhiu  kin cho rng cn c mt chnh sch tin lng, tin thng minh bch, cng bng v hp dn mi c th thu ht cng nh gi chn ngi lao ng. </span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;">Doanh nghip cn xy dng mi trng cng tc hiu qua bao gm lnh o n trng, minh bch nhn s, c s vt cht m bo, ch  thng cnh tranh, c hi thng tin r rng. ng u Thanh Tng, Gim c Nhn s Cng ty u t Thy Dng lu , cc ch doanh nghip khng nn ly l do bn rn  ri y quyn cho b phn khc trc tip phng vn, tuyn dng nhn s cho cng ty.  ch l ngy bin cho s cha coi trng cng tc tuyn ngi.</span></div>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;">V cch thc gi nhn ti, ng Chris Havey, CEO mng tm kim vic lm VietnamWorks v Navigos Search nhn mnh, mi lnh o cng ty phi thng xuyn ni chuyn vi nhn vin ca mnh, trong khi ni chuyn phi gn mc tiu ca mi c nhn vi mc tiu ln ca cng ty v cho h thy, ch doanh nghip lun h tr  h t c mc ch ngh nghip ca mnh./. </span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: right;" class="news_author"><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><strong>(Ngun TTXVN/Vietnam+)</strong><br /></span></div>', '', 1, 3, 0, 22, '2011-12-19 09:48:33', 62, '', '2011-12-22 18:03:39', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-12-19 09:46:20', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 4, 0, 2, '', '', 0, 46, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(78, 'Mt gio vin Vit Nam ot gii Gio vin th gii', 'mt-giao-vien-vit-nam-ot-gii-giao-vien-th-gii', '', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="pTitle">Mt gio vin Vit Nam ot gii Gio vin th gii</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="pHead">TTO -&nbsp;Vn phng Vin Bell International ca Vng quc Anh ti TP.HCM va thng bo: c L Xun Hng, gio vin ting Anh ca trng THCS Tn Ho (x Tn Ho, huyn Ging Trm, Bn Tre) ot gii nht gio vin th gii do Hi ng kho th ting Anh ca trng i hc Cambridge Vng quc Anh chm gii.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="pBody">C Hng l gio vin duy nht ti Vit Nam v l mt trong 5 gio vin trn th gii ot gii ny. Vi gii gio vin th gii, c Hng s c ti tr hc bng 200 bng Anh  d&nbsp;kha hc pht trin ti nng ging dy dnh cho gio vin ca vin Bell Internationnal ch dnh cho 5 gio vin trn th gii. Kha hc s khai ging vo ngy 18-7 nm nay.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="pBody">C Hng cho bit khi c Ban gim hiu ph bin vn bn v cuc thi gio vin th gii, c ngh mnh c th tham gia cuc thi v c  vit mt bi vit 150 t bng ting Anh, miu t nhng li ch mang li cho gio vin v hc sinh khi tham d nhng chng trnh nng cao nghip v gio vin.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="pBody">C Hng l gio vin tt nghip trng cao ng s phm Bn Tre, tnh nguyn v x vng su ging dy trong 10 nm nay.</p>', '', 1, 3, 0, 19, '2011-12-18 06:16:25', 62, '', '2011-12-22 18:03:24', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-12-18 06:15:52', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 2, 0, 2, '', '', 0, 32, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(79, 'Trin khai 7  n i mi ngnh s phm', 'trin-khai-7--an-i-mi-nganh-s-phm', '', '<p></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="pTitle">Trin khai 7  n i mi ngnh s phm</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="pHead">TT - B trng B GD-T Phm V Lun va k quyt nh ph duyt Chng trnh pht trin ngnh s phm v cc trng s phm t nm 2011-2020.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="pBody"><img style="float: left;" src="data/giaoduc/photo/nu_sinh.jpg" alt="alt" width="297" height="197" />Mc tiu chng trnh nhm xy dng cc trng i hc s phm tr thnh cc trung tm sng to, i mi cn bn v ton din ngnh s phm c nc; tng cng s gn kt gia h thng cc trng, khoa s phm vi h thng gio dc mm non, gio dc ph thng v cc cp qun l gio dc  bo m s ng b trong xy dng v trin khai thc hin chng trnh gio dc mm non mi v chng trnh gio dc ph thng sau nm 2015.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;" class="pBody"> thc hin vic ny, chng trnh s c by  n gm: cng c mng li c s o to gio vin, tng cng c s vt cht ca cc trng s phm; pht trin i ng ging vin cc trng, khoa s phm, i mi cng tc qun l v iu hnh cc c s o to gio vin; nng cao vai tr ca cc trng s phm trong cng tc pht trin i ng gio vin mm non, ph thng, gio dc thng xuyn; tng cng vai tr ca cc trng s phm trong cng tc bi dng hiu trng trng mm non, ph thng v gim c trung tm gio dc thng xuyn v cng chc s, phng gio dc v o to; nng cao cht lng hot ng khoa hc cng ngh v hp tc quc t ca cc trng s phm v kim nh cht lng cc trng s phm.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;" class="pBody"><strong>(Tui tr)</strong></p>', '', 1, 3, 0, 22, '2011-12-18 06:18:16', 62, '', '2012-03-16 06:52:37', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-12-18 06:17:07', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 3, 0, 1, '', '', 0, 36, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(80, 'Thn ng vn hc', 'thn-ng-vn-hc', '', '<p style="text-align: left;"><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Thn ng vn hc</span></strong></p>\r\n<div class="VB_gioi_thieu200" style="text-align: justify;">\r\n<div class="VB_gioi_thieu">C cho rng Nguyn Bnh vo mng ko tt tn tt nhng kin thc ca nhn loi xung ri ghp li thnh mt cu chuyn hp dn nh Cuc chin vi hnh tinh Fantom, i vi mt cu b 9 tui  l qu gii.\r\n<div class="baivietMainBox-img200" style="text-align: left;"><img alt="Thn ng vn hc" class="thumb-border" src="http://a9.vietbao.vn/images/vi955/2011/12/55425594-1324173104_nguyen-binh1.jpg" style="float: right; width: 168px; height: 168px;" /></div>\r\n<div style="float: right;">\r\n<div id="google_ads_div_vbb7.1_ad_container">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Ngy 16-12-2011, Nguyn Bnh trn 10 tui. Nu con trai ti chu lp gia nh sm th chu ni ti cng c tui nh Bnh. Nhng  bi vit ny, ti xem Bnh l mt ng nghip, v chu l tc gi ca mt tp sch y n v s trang ln ni dung: Cuc chin vi hnh tinh Fantom, do NXB Tr v NXB Hng Bng va n hnh.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Duyn khi</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Gp nhau  TPHCM, nh th Trn ng Khoa  ngh ti tm c Nguyn Bnh xem th c ging suy ngh ca anh khng. Mi u, ti tng  l hi k ca v tng ni danh mt thi  Nam B nhng Trn ng Khoa ci chnh: Nguyn Bnh l mt cu b c bit!. Thy ti cha my hiu, Khoa k cho ti nghe v Nguyn Bnh, con trai t ca nh ph bnh vn hc Nguyn Ha.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Nguyn Bnh bit ni rnh rt t khi mi mi my thng tui; 3 tui  c thng bit tho v  bit lm quen vi my vi tnh, in thoi di ng; 4 tui  bit nhn tin cho b mua cun t in Hn Vit N cn t hc c ting Anh mi khip ch! Chic my vi tnh l ng thy ln ca n. T ch bit trnh  ting Anh ca Bnh ti u m n dch c phim na kia. Hm no v, t gi vo cho bc my ci phim n download trn mng xung ri dch v thuyt minh. T xem phim, nghe li thoi v thy hay. Th l gii, bc  - Trn ng Khoa thn phc.</p>\r\n', '\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Ti ha sng mai i mua cun Cuc chin vi hnh tinh Fantom v s c  kin ngay. Lc y, anh Nguyn Ha n (Nguyn Ha v Trn ng Khoa cng d hi tho  TPHCM). Anh lin gi xe m ra nh sch mang v cun sch ca con cn thm mi mc in v Thay mt chu tng bc Vu Gia. Ni theo nh Pht, y l duyn khi. Nhn s lng pht hnh 5.000 cun, nhng ngi cm bt trn t nc ny khng ai khng thm.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Rt ng trn trng</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Con ci l tng lai ca cha m nn ti khng ch trn trng n nhn tc phm u tay ca ng nghip nh tui m cn trn trng n nhn c nim vui lm cha ca anh Nguyn Ha. Chu Bnh pht tit anh hoa khi mi vi ba tui m n nay ngi ta mi bit n,  thy anh nn nim vui y lu lm.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">c xong hn 170 trang sch (kh 13 x 20 cm), ti thy Nguyn Bnh dn dt ngi c ht i t Hy Lp n M ri sang  vi nhng chi tit hp dn. Tn ngi, tn t rt c th v rt ng. Nguyn Bnh dch t truyn nc ngoi ? Nu y l bn dch th cng l bn dch hay. Nu chuyn ng (hoc phng tc) m din t nh th, khng phi ai gii ngoi ng cng lm c.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Bt c d qu chng ti mi dng my bay. T lc i n gi, duy nht mt ln ti i tu thy, cn li l my bay. Ch ti my a bn ti. Ti  nh i tu in ngm t Greenland v m bn n c khng khng ni rng i my bay thch hn. M cng ch ti ht v tu in ngm, ch khng ti cng i tu in ngm t lu ri!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Ny Frank! Ngm ngh g th?  Philippe hi.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Ti mc k cu ta, y ci gh v pha sau v nm ng. nh trng chiu ri vo chic my bay, ging ci cnh chic trc thng Apache b nh sng ca mt trng chiu trc tip vo (trang 114).<br /> <br /> Vi ci tn Frank, Nguyn Bnh gii thiu cng kh th v: Ti tn l Frank William Wells. Bn bit khng, ti  tng rt ght ci tn ca mnh. Ti sao khng phi l Harry nh Harry Potter, George nh George Washington, Christopher nh Christopher Colombus m li l Frank, mt ci tn cng chng c g c bit? Ti  nhiu ln ni n b m cho i tn, nhng b m khng chu, v b l fan cung nhit ca cu th bng  ngi Anh Frank Lampard.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><img alt="Thn ng vn hc, Tin tc trong ngy, giao duc, tieu thuyet, than dong, van hoc, bao" class="news-image" src="http://a9.vietbao.vn/images/vi955/2011/12/55425594-1324173008-nguyen-binh2.jpg" height="422" width="563" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #0000ff;"><em>Thn ng Nguyn Bnh (gia - hng u) giao lu vi c gi ti TPHCM mi y.</em></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Cn m lun m c ti tr thnh mt ngi v i nh tng thng Franklin D. Roosevelt. Lm ngi lnh o th cng sng tht, (nh hin ti ti cng l th lnh ny) nhng l do ln nht khin ti khng a c ci tn Frank l v n lm ti lin tng ti con qui vt Frankenstein. Ti xem b phim v con qui vt  nm 4 tui, d cha hiu lm nhng ti  khc tht ln trong phng khch khi b mt kinh d ca con qui vt hin ln trn mn hnh.<br /> <br /> Mi my nm sau, khi ti trn 7 tui, ln u t chn ti thnh ph Los Angeles, ti mi bit mnh c cng tn vi kin trc s M Frank Gehry, ngi  thit k nh ht c kin trc k cc Walt Disney (Walt Disney Concert Hall), nh ht ni ti sut ng gt v khc do u (overture) ca v opera Romeo v Juliet. T , ti hi lng v ci tn ca mnh v b hn  nh i tn (trang 18-19).</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Cun sch ny Nguyn Bnh vit t u nm 2011 bng my vi tnh ca m. L mt a b bnh thng nh mi a tr cng  tui ngy ngy m v ti trng, Nguyn Bnh ch vit vo nhng ngy ngh v nhng lc c nh bn bu cng vic. Ngi nh thy Bnh ngi vo my khng chi game l vui ri, chng ai quan tm cu cu lm g. n lc nhn bn tho (Nguyn Bnh t dn trang v minh ha ra dng mt cun sch), anh Nguyn Ha mi ng ngi v cng khng hiu g, bn nh bn b c gip, trong  c cu thn ng Trn ng Khoa.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Khng c g khin cng</strong><br /> <br /> Vi cch dng truyn nh th, kin vn nh th, bn thn ti khng lm c, d mang ting xut bn gn 30 u sch, trong  c nhiu sch bin kho. C cho rng Nguyn Bnh vo mng ko tt tn tt nhng kin thc ca nhn loi xung ri ghp li thnh mt cu chuyn hp dn nh Cuc chin vi hnh tinh Fantom, th cng l qu gii.<br /> <br /> Ch cn cp nht kin thc  gii thiu bn thn mnh nh on trch  trn, vi ti  l gii lm. Mt lun vn thc s, v c bn ch yu cu hc vin bit c cch tng hp v phn tch t liu cn thit cho  ti  chun b bc ng k tip (nu mun), ch u cn phi c c sng nh yu cu ca lun n tin s. Do , gi Nguyn Bnh l thn ng vn hc cng khng c g khin cng.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">y mi l tp 1 ca nhiu tp trong Cuc chin vi hnh tinh Fantom. Nhng nhn vt ngi tri t nh Frank William Wells, Michael John Henderson, George Abraham Carroll, Sarah Margaret Adams, Nguyn Bnh u cho sinh vo nm 2005, vi a ch v s thch c th. Ngi  hnh tinh Bng Ma nh Bejeweled, Cakkatge, Nguyn Bnh cho sinh vo khong nm 1940, vi s thch v k lc kh hp dn:</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">S thch ca Bejeweled: La o (bng chng: tng bo nhm Earth ti Greenland chng v mc ch g); xm chim mt hnh tinh c s sng  mt thin h khc; nhng th trong truyn thuyt, v d Chn Thnh v Hm Giao c ( tng ni: Nu ta chim c Tri t, ta s bt loi ngi cc ngi tm y  nhng vt truyn thuyt  cho ta, cng vi vic giao np ht tt c s vng bc m cc ngi s hu t bui bnh minh ti nay!); K lc:  tng chim c Sao Mc, hnh tinh ln nht h Mt Tri v quay tr v thin h ca hn vi hai bn tay trng. K lc ca Cakkratge:  tng bp bm ngi Tri t ht mc c th bng cch tr v qu kh v gy ra v ng  UFO  Roswll, New Mexico nm 1947 (trang 13)</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Cch lp l lch trch ngang ny, ti thy Nht Linh cng thc hin trong truyn di Xm Cu Mi cch nay hn na th k. Th nhng, ti tin Nguyn Bnh khng bit Nht Linh l ai.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Nhng cuc khm ph cng nhng trn chin xy ra  a ch c th, vi mt thi gian cng rt c th l nm 2015. Ngha l ch cn 4 nm na thi. iu ny rt th v nhng cng tht bt li cho tc gi. Nhng nh th mi l Nguyn Bnh - nh th Trn ng Khoa nhn xt.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>9 tui sao vit c nh th?</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Trn ng Khoa cho rng Nguyn Bnh c vong nh vn nc ngoi no  nhp, ch lm sao a b 9 tui vit c nh th? Gi  ca Trn ng Khoa lm ti phi suy ngh. Trong Pht thoi c ni: Dc tri tin th nhn/ Kim sinh th gi th (Mun bit kip trc, hy xem i sng hin ti). Vy anh hoa pht tit ca Nguyn Bnh do tin kip ?</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Thng tun thng 12-2011, ni chuyn vi sinh vin  H Ni, GS Trnh Xun Thun, nh thin vn hc ni ting th gii, cho bit ng tin khi vt cht cht i, linh hn vn tn ti nhng tn ti  u th ng khng bit, v ngay c khoa hc cng khng tr li ni. Ti mang chuyn ny n gp TS - Thng ta Thch ng Bn, quyn tr tr cha Pht hc X Li - TPHCM. Thng ta cho rng Nguyn Bnh c nh vy l nh hun tp t nhiu kip</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">L ngi cha, nay con ci cng  phng trng nn ti rt hy vng anh Nguyn Ha tha kh nng gip con mnh suy ngh v hnh ng tch cc  chu thy vng vng trong cc tnh hung gp phi trn bc ng trng thnh. Kinh Dch c ni: Nhc yu hu tin trnh, mc t mt tin trnh (Nu tht c no trc mt ta, th ch nn lm mt no y).</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><img alt="" class="contenttoc" dir="ltr" src="images/hinhanh/lo go veritable 2.jpg" style="float: left;" /></span></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;">&nbsp;<strong>vietbao</strong></p>', 1, 4, 0, 25, '2011-12-16 17:00:00', 62, '', '2011-12-22 17:55:08', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-12-16 17:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 18, 0, 2, '', '', 0, 47, 'robots=\nauthor='),
