(98, 'Thng t ban hnh quy ch nh gi, xp loi hc sinh THCS v hc sinh THPT', 'thong-t-ban-hanh-quy-ch-anh-gia-xp-loi-hc-sinh-thcs-va-hc-sinh-thpt', '', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="arialTitle">Thng t ban hnh quy ch nh gi, xp loi hc sinh THCS v hc sinh THPT</p>\r\n<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr class="txtNhodi">\r\n<td>S t liu:</td>\r\n<td><b>58/2011/TT-BGDT</b></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class="txtNhodi">\r\n<td>Ngy ban hnh:</td>\r\n<td><b>15-12-2011</b></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr class="txtNhodi">\r\n<td>Tp nh km:</td>\r\n<td><b><img src="http://www.moet.gov.vn/images/doc.gif" align="absmiddle" /> <a>58-2011-TT.doc</a></b></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Cn c Lut Gio dc ngy 14 thng 6 nm 2005; Lut sa i, b sung mt s iu ca Lut Gio dc ngy 25 thng 11 nm 2009;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Cn c Ngh nh s 32/2008/N-CP ngy 19 thng 3 nm 2008 ca Chnh ph quy nh chc nng, nhim v, quyn hn v c cu t chc ca B Gio dc v o to;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Cn c Ngh nh s 75/2006/N-CP ngy 02 thng 8 nm 2006 ca Chnh ph quy nh chi tit v hng dn thi hnh mt s iu ca Lut Gio dc; Ngh nh s 31/2011/N-CP ngy 11 thng 5 nm 2011 ca Chnh ph sa i, b sung mt s iu ca Ngh nh s 75/2006/N-CP ngy 02 thng 8 nm 2006 ca Chnh ph quy nh chi tit v hng dn thi hnh mt s iu ca Lut Gio dc;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Theo  ngh ca V trng V Gio dc Trung hc,</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">B trng B Gio dc v o to quyt nh:</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><b>iu 1.</b> Ban hnh km theo Thng t ny Quy ch nh gi, xp loi hc sinh trung hc c s v hc sinh trung hc ph thng.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><b>iu 2.</b> Thng t ny c hiu lc thi hnh k t ngy 26 thng 01 nm 2012. Thng t ny thay th Quyt nh s 40/2006/Q-BGDT ngy 05 thng 10 nm 2006 ca B trng B Gio dc v o to ban hnh Quy ch nh gi, xp loi hc sinh trung hc c s v hc sinh trung hc ph thng v Thng t s 51/2008/Q-BGDT ngy 15/9/2008 ca B trng B Gio dc v o to sa i, b sung mt s iu ca Quy ch nh gi, xp loi hc sinh trung hc c s v hc sinh trung hc ph thng ban hnh km theo Quyt nh s 40/2006/Q-BGDT ngy 05 thng 10 nm 2006 ca B trng B Gio dc v o to.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><b>iu 3. </b>Chnh Vn phng, V trng V Gio dc Trung hc, Th trng cc n v c lin quan thuc B Gio dc v o to, Ch tch y ban nhn dn tnh, thnh ph trc thuc trung ng, Gim c S Gio dc v o to chu trch nhim thi hnh Thng t ny./.</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: xx-small;"><b><i>Ni nhn:</i></b><br /> - Vn phng Quc hi ( bo co);<br /> - Vn phng Chnh ph ( bo co);<br /> - U ban VHGD TNTNN ca Quc hi ( bo co);&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br /> - Ban Tuyn gio Trung ng ( bo co);<br /> - B trng Phm V Lun ( bo co);<br /> - Cc Kim tra vn bn QPPL (B T php);<br /> - UBND cc tnh, thnh ph trc thuc TW&nbsp;( thc hin);<br /> - Nh iu 3;<br /> - Cng bo;<br /> - Website Chnh ph;<br /> - Website B GD&amp;T;<br /> - Lu VT, V PC, V GDTrH.</span></p>', '', 1, 2, 0, 15, '2012-02-07 17:00:00', 62, '', '2012-04-08 08:22:48', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-02-07 17:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 4, 0, 1, '', '', 0, 37, 'robots=\nauthor='),
(99, 'Gii thiu chung', 'gii-thiu-chung', '', '<p style="text-align: justify; line-height: 120%;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: 10pt;"><b><span style="color: black;"><span style="color: #993300;">* M hnh nh trng:</span> </span></b></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; line-height: 120%;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 120%; font-family: times new roman,times;"> Trng THPT Phan Huy Ch ng a l trng THPT Cng Lp duy nht ca Thnh ph H Ni hot ng theo m hnh <span style="color: black;">Trng cng lp t ch ti chnh ton phn theo Ngh nh 43 ca Chnh ph, c ngha l trng c cp c s vt cht ban u khng c cp ngn sch v phi t ch, t chu trch nhim v thc hin nhim v, t chc b my, bin ch v ti chnh. Vic chi cho mi hot ng ca nh trng trong 12 thng u ly t ngun qu hc ph ca hc sinh trong 9 thng, k c lng v bo him x hi ca i ng bin ch cng nh sa cha, bo dng, duy tr c s vt cht...</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; line-height: 120%;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: 10pt;"><b><span style="line-height: 120%;"><span style="color: #993300;">* C s vt cht:</span> </span></b></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; line-height: 120%;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 120%; font-family: times new roman,times;">- Nh trng c mi trng s phm l tng, khun vin rng p gn 10.000m<sup>2</sup>, nm gia khu dn c tri thc v yn tnh, c nn np k cng dy v hc. Vi khun vin l tng  l iu kin thun li  nh trng t chc cc hot ng ngoi kha nhm pht huy tnh tch cc v kh nng ca hc sinh, xy dng mi trng thn thin.Th vin ca nh trng c nhiu hot ng sng to vi 15.000 u sch c cng nhn l Th vin xut sc (duy nht cp THPT) ca Thnh ph. </span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; line-height: 120%;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 120%; font-family: times new roman,times;">- 100% phng hc v phng hp ca trng  c trang b my chiu, mn chiu, h thng rm ca, nh sng. Hu ht gio vin t trang b my tnh xch tay  ch ng vic son bi v kt ni vi my chiu trong bt c phng hc no khi ging dy cng nh khi hp chuyn mn, hp ph huynh, hi tho hay gi sinh hot. Vic ng dng CNTT trong i mi dy hc cng nh trong hot ng gio dc  tr thnh thi quen v nhu cu khng th thiu ca c gio vin v hc sinh nh trng.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; line-height: 120%;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: 10pt; color: #993300;"><b><span style="line-height: 120%;">* Cht lng gio dc:</span></b></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; line-height: 120%;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 120%; color: black; font-family: times new roman,times;">- T l  tt nghip hng nm lun vt t l chung ca Thnh ph (thp nht l 98%)</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; line-height: 120%;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 120%; color: black; font-family: times new roman,times;">- T l hc sinh  vo cc trng H, C ngy cng cao, nhiu hc sinh  th khoa,  khoa vo cc trng i hc. Nm 2009, <span style="line-height: 120%;">hc sinh Nguyn Hong Phng 12B3 Th khoa Trng i hc KHXH &NV, Nguyn Thanh Sn 12B3  Th khoa H Sn khu in nh, V Phng Chu 12B4 -  khoa Trng i hc S phm H Ni. <span style="color: black;">c bit, lp cht lng cao 12A0 c 29/30 hc sinh  vo i hc cng lp c danh ting trong  8 HS  2 trng tng ng vi 2 khi thi, tiu biu l hc sinh Trnh Tun Sn  29,5 im trng i hc Ngoi thng (  khoa ) v 24,5 im trng i hc Y H Ni. M hnh cc lp cht lng cao s ngy cng c nhn rng  tin ti xy dng nh trng theo m hnh <i>Cung ng dch v gio dc cht lng cao</i></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; line-height: 120%;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 120%; color: black; font-family: times new roman,times;">- Thi hc sinh gii Thnh ph, nm no cng c hc sinh tham gia v t gii cao. c bit, nm hc 2008-2009 v 2009-2010 mi nm c 7 hc sinh t gii/ 16 hc sinh tham gia thi.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; line-height: 120%;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 120%; color: black; font-family: times new roman,times;">- T nm 2003 n nay, cc cuc thi gio vin gii ca Thnh ph, nm hc no cng c gio vin c vo vng 2 v t gii cao.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; line-height: 120%;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 120%; font-family: times new roman,times;">- Phong tro vn ngh v TDTT l hot ng si ni trong nh trng, vi 115 huy chng cc gii th thao trong v ngoi nc, 7 nm lin tc nh trng c cng nhn l Trng Tin tin xut sc v TDTT. Cc sn chi, bi tp ca hc sinh c nng cp, sa cha, cc em lun trn y ho hng v thng xuyn c tham ga hot ng ngoi kha vui v b ch. Th vin ca nh trng c nhiu hot ng sng to vi 15.000 u sch c cng nhn l Th vin xut sc (duy nht cp THPT) ca Thnh ph. </span></p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 120%; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: 10pt; color: #993300;"><b><span style="line-height: 120%;">* Cng tc tuyn sinh:</span></b></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; line-height: 120%;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 120%; font-family: times new roman,times;">- Ch tiu: Nm hc 2011- 2012 trng c tuyn sinh 9 lp 10 (gn 400 hc sinh), trong  c 4 lp cht lng cao (2 lp c bn A, 2 lp c bn D ).</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; line-height: 120%;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 120%; font-family: times new roman,times;">- Phng thc tuyn sinh: Khng t chc thi tuyn m xt tuyn da theo im tuyn sinh ca hc sinh cng lp (i vi hc sinh H Ni) v xt tuyn trn hc b (vi hc sinh kh gii ca tnh ngoi). </span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; line-height: 120%;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 120%; font-family: times new roman,times;">- Song song vi vic tuyn sinh u cp, nh trng vn tip nhn nhng hc sinh t trng khc v tnh khc chuyn v vi iu kin: kt qu  trng c phi t hnh kim kh v hc lc kh tr ln, ng thi hc sinh xin chuyn v phi qua kho st cht lng 2 mn Vn v Ton.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: times new roman,times;"></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: right;" align="center"><span style="font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: 10pt;