(102, 'HNG TI MT MI TRNG GIO DC TON DIN, CHT LNG CAO', 'hng-ti-mt-moi-trng-giao-dc-toan-din-cht-lng-cao', '', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #000000; font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: 12pt;"> Trong xu th hi nhp v pht trin nhanh nh hin nay, nhim v ca gio dc ph thng l trang b nhng hnh trang thit yu cho hc sinh  chuyn b cho hc sinh vng tin bc vo giai on mi ca cuc sng. Trc mc tiu , Trng THPT Phan Huy Ch lun <strong>"HNG TI MT MI TRNG GIO DC TON DIN, CHT LNG CAO"</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #000000; font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: 12pt;"><b><img style="float: left;" src="data/giaoduc/d0bhocvan1.jpg" alt="alt" height="156" width="209" />1.</b><b>Tng cng c s vt cht:</b></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; font-family: times new roman,times;">Ngy 28/4/10, UBND Thnh ph H Ni  ban hnh Quyt nh s 1936/Q-UBND ph duyt d n u t xy dng Trng THPT Phan Huy Ch - ng a nhm tng cng c s vt cht theo tiu chun trng chun quc gia v nng cao cht lng dy hc. D n c tng mc u t 41.249 triu ng, ngun vn ngn sch Thnh ph cp.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #000000; font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: 12pt;">Ni dung u t d n: Xy mi nh hc 5 tng vi din tch mt bng 4.990m2; nh Gio dc th cht vi din tch 648m2; nh cng - tin vi din tch 110m2; ci to nh Hiu b, cc cng trnh h tng ph tr v trang thit b dy hc.<b></b></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #000000; font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: 12pt;"><b>2.</b> M hnh hot ng:<b></b></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #000000; font-family: times new roman,times; font-size: 12pt;"><b>a.</b><b> Cung ng dch v gio dc cht lng cao</b></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; font-family: times new roman,times;">-<span style="font-style: normal; font-