(114, 'Khi 12 kho 2009-2012', 'khi-12-khoa-2009-2012', '', '<p></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Khi 12 kho 13 (2009-2012) ca trng Phan Huy Ch-ng a</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Vo trng t thng 7 nm 2009, n nay ch cn cha y 2 thng na, khi 12 kho th 13 ca mi trng Phan Huy Ch sp chia tay thy c v bn b.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Nh n chim sp tung cnh bay vo bu tri bao la. Nhng ngy nng p ang ch n v c nhng th thch cng ang mong i kho 13, vt ln  khng nh mnh.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Khi 12 nm hc 2011-2012 c quy m gn nh so vi cc khi 12 trc v c l c sau. C khi c 6 lp 12: 12A1, 12A2, 12A3 v 12D1, 12D2, 12D3.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Trong , c 3 lp c bn ban A v 3 lp c bn ban D,  l mt i hnh cn xng kh th v:</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Lp 12 A1 vi 25 hc sinh, do c gio Bi Thu Cc lm ch nhim<br />Lp 12 A2 vi 41 hc sinh, do thy gio Phng Tun Vit lm ch nhim<br />Lp 12 A3 vi 43 hc sinh, do thy gio Nguyn Minh c lm ch nhim</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Lp 12 D1 vi 23 hc sinh, do c gio Nguyn Kim Anh lm ch nhim<br />Lp 12 D2 vi 42 hc sinh, do c gio L Th Hng Hnh lm ch nhim<br />Lp 12 D3 vi 46 hc sinh, do thy gio H Vn Th lm ch nhim</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Trong khi, c hai lp cht lng cao ban 12 A1 v 12 D1.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Cng him c khi l2 no (k c trong v ngoi trng Phan Huy Ch-ng a) m s thy- c gio ch nhim li cn nh vy:<br />- Su lp th ba lp c thy gio v ba lp c c gio lm ch nhim<br />- Ba thy c dy Ton, hai c gio dy Vn v mt thy gio dy Vt l  cng v ch nhim lp.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Khi 12 nm nay tp hp nhng hc sinh sinh nm 1994, tui Tut vi nt tnh cch chung l nng nhit, thng thn v bit phc thin.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Nhng ngy n tp vt v ang bt u, nhng dng ch vit ln c m ca hc sinh 6 lp 12 nm nay cng ang lp lnh nt mc trn h s d thi. Cc tr ang ghi tn cc trng i hc v Cao ng m mi em ang ao c trng tuyn trong k thi thng 7/2012.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">C Hiu trng v cc thy c ch nhim va c cuc hp vi cc bc ph huynh v vic n thi tt nghip ca hc sinh khi 12 nm hc ny.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Trc mt ca cc tr lp 12 nm nay ang l nhng k thi, nhng chn tri rng m. Ngi ngn ni ra, nhng hc tr khi 12 kho ny s tip bc cc th h i trc v thm ha s xng vi mong i ca cha m, nhng lo lng ca cc thy c gio!</p>', '', 1, 1, 0, 9, '2012-04-03 09:42:03', 85, '', '2012-04-03 13:05:25', 66, 62, '2012-04-06 06:44:01', '2012-04-03 09:36:07', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', '', 3, 0, 1, 'Khi 12, 2009-2012, 12A1, 12D1, 12A2, 12A3, 12D2, 12D3', '', 0, 4, ''),
(115, 'Tuyn sinh nm hc 2012-2013', 'tuyn-sinh-nm-hc-2012-2013', '', '<p style="text-align: center;" align="center"><b><span style="color: black; font-family: ''UVnSouthern'',''serif''; font-size: 17pt;">TRNG THPT PHAN HUY CH  NG A</span></b></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;" align="center"><b><span style="color: black; font-family: ''UVnSouthern'',''serif''; font-size: 17pt;">&nbsp;</span></b></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><b><i><span style="font-size: 14pt;">a ch: S 34- Ng 49- Hunh Thc Khng  Qun ng a  H Ni.</span></i></b></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><b><i><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Website: <a href="http://www.phc.edu.vn">http://www.phc.edu.vn</a></span></i></b><b><i><span style="font-size: 14pt;"></span></i></b></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><b><i><span style="font-size: 14pt;">in thoi: 04.37730751- 04.37731514</span></i></b><b><i><span style="font-size: 14pt;"></span></i></b></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><b><i><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><span style="text-decoration: none;">&nbsp;</span></span></i></b></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; line-height: 120%;"><b><span style="line-height: 120%; font-size: 13pt;">1. M hnh nh trng:</span></b></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; line-height: 120%; text-indent: 0.5in;"><span style="line-height: 120%; font-size: 13pt;">L trng THPT cng lp hot ng theo m hnh <b><i><span style="color: black;">Cng lp t ch ti chnh ton phn</span></i></b><span style="color: black;"> theo Ngh nh 43 ca Chnh ph v thc hin chng trnh 07/CTr-TU ca Thnh y H Ni, trng ang tin n m hnh <b><i>Cung ng dch v gio dc trnh  cht lng cao </i></b>theo xu hng gio dc hin i tin tin.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; line-height: 120%; text-indent: 0.5in;"><span style="line-height: 120%; font-size: 13pt;">Do vy mc hc ph ca nh trng c thu trn s tha thun vi ph huynh hc sinh v c php ca Thnh ph.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; line-height: 120%;"><b><span style="line-height: 120%; font-size: 13pt;">2. Mt nn tng c xy dng cho s pht trin ton din</span></b></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; line-height: 120%;"><b><span style="line-height: 120%; font-size: 13pt;"> * C s vt cht: </span></b><span style="line-height: 120%; font-size: 13pt;">Nh trng c mi trng s phm l tng, khun vin rng 10.000m<sup>2</sup> nm gia khu dn c tri thc v yn tnh gm 1 khu nh hc 5 tng c trang b cc phng tin dy hc hin i, c  cc phng hc b mn; 1 Th vin xut sc cp Thnh ph rng 300 m<sup>2 </sup>vi trn 15.000 u sch v nhiu hot ng sng to; 1 nh Th cht rng gn 500m<sup>2</sup>, sn chi v sn bng r l ni vui chi, luyn tp th thao ca hc sinh; 1 nh cng tin, 1 phng y t phc v v chm sc.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; line-height: 120%;"><b><span style="line-height: 120%; font-size: 13pt;"> * i ng cn b qun l: </span></b><span style="line-height: 120%; font-size: 13pt;">100% trnh  trn chun, c tm, c tm, st sao, sng to v khoa hc.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; line-height: 120%;"><b><span style="line-height: 120%; font-size: 13pt;"> * i ng gio vin: </span></b><span style="line-height: 120%; font-size: 13pt;">50% i ng gio vin, trong  87% i ng gio vin bin ch c trnh  trn chun; c bit tn tm ging dy, tch cc i mi phng php dy v hc theo hng hin i ha, qun l st sao, chm sc tt nht v mi mt  hc tr pht trin ton din.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; line-height: 120%;"><span style="line-height: 120%; font-size: 13pt;"> <b>*Dy ch song song vi Dy ngi:</b> a dng ha cc hot ng ngoi kha vn th nhm rn k nng sng, pht huy tnh tch cc, sng to ca hc sinh, xy dng mi trng thn thin.<b></b></span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; line-height: 120%;"><b><span style="color: black; line-height: 120%; font-size: 13pt;">3. Cht lng gio dc  c thm nh:</span></b></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; line-height: 120%; text-indent: 0.5in;"><span style="color: black; line-height: 120%; font-size: 13pt;">- T l  tt nghip hng nm lun vt t l chung ca Thnh ph (thp nht l 98%). Nm 2011 t l  tt nghip l 99,8%.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; line-height: 120%; text-indent: 0.5in;"><span style="color: black; line-height: 120%; font-size: 13pt;">- T l hc sinh  vo cc trng H, C ngy cng cao. T nm 2005 n nay  c 6 hc sinh  Th khoa v  khoa cc trng i hc cng lp c danh ting. Nm 2011 t l  i hc l 38%, trong  cc lp cht lng cao  97%.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; line-height: 120%; text-indent: 0.5in;"><span style="color: black; line-height: 120%; font-size: 13pt;">- Hng nm nh trng lun c cc gii cao trong k thi Hc sinh gii Thnh ph.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; line-height: 120%; text-indent: 0.5in;"><span style="color: black; line-height: 120%; font-size: 13pt;">- Nh trng c truyn thng nhiu nm lin tc c gio vin c nhn gii cao trrong cc k thi gio vin dy gii cp Thnh ph.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; line-height: 120%;"><b><span style="line-height: 120%; font-size: 13pt;">4. Cng tc tuyn sinh</span></b></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify; line-height: 120%; text-indent: 0.5in;"><span style="line-height: 120%; font-size: 13pt;">- Nm hc 2012- 2013 nh trng tuyn sinh 8 lp, trong  t chc 4 lp cht lng cao (2 lp tuyn chn, 2 lp nhu cu). Cc lp cht lng cao c u t v i ng gio vin, chng trnh hc v c s vt cht. Mi lp khong 35 hc sinh, hc 2 bui/ngy, n ng tra ti trng (nu c nhu cu<b>).</b></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; font-size: 13pt;">- Nhng hc sinh c im xt tuyn t 50 im tr ln v c t nht 3 nm cp THCS t hc sinh gii c xt thng vo lp cht lng cao tuyn chn. Nhng hc sinh khc nu c nguyn vng hc lp cht lng cao phi  tiu chun sau khi kho st.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; font-size: 13pt;"><img src="data/giaoduc/Untitled-3.jpg" alt="" height="263" width="388" /></span></p>', '', 1, 2, 0, 17, '2012-04-04 02:18:22', 66, '', '2012-04-10 03:12:57', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-04-04 02:16:35', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 4, 0, 1, '', 'PHC, Phan Huy Ch, tuyn sinh 2012-2013, ng a', 0, 22, 'robots=\nauthor=');
